#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:48
msgid ""
"Next is the :guilabel:`Prompt` field. In Odoo, :ref:`prompts <ai/agents/"
"prompts-in-odoo>` define the instructions that guide the |AI| when "
"generating or improving the content of the |AI| field. The prompt tells the "
"system what kind of information to produce, how to format it, and what tone "
"or style to use."
msgstr ""
"Næste er feltet :guilabel:`Prompt`. I Odoo definerer :ref:`prompts <ai/"
"agents/prompts-in-odoo>` de instruktioner, der guider |AI|, når systemet "
"genererer eller forbedrer indholdet af |AI|-feltet. Prompten fortæller "
"systemet, hvilken type information der skal produceres, hvordan den skal "
"formateres, og hvilken tone eller stil der skal bruges."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:53
msgid ""
"When creating a prompt, use the `/field` command to reference specific "
"fields in the database. For example, to reference the :guilabel:`Company` "
"field on a record, enter `/field`, and click the :guilabel:`Field Selector` "
"option. Type `Company` in the search bar, and select :guilabel:`Company` "
"from the list."
msgstr ""
"Når du opretter en prompt, skal du bruge kommandoen `/field` til at referere "
"til specifikke felter i databasen. For eksempel skal du for at referere til "
"feltet :guilabel:`Virksomhed` på en post indtaste `/field` og klikke på "
"indstillingen :guilabel:`Feltvælger`. Indtast `Company` i søgefeltet, og "
"vælg :guilabel:`Virksomhed` fra listen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:None
msgid "The add a field pop-up where the ai prompt is entered."
msgstr "Pop-up til tilføjelse af felt, hvor KI-prompten indtastes."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:61
msgid ""
"Once the prompt is complete, click :guilabel:`Add Field`. Before closing "
"**Studio**, click on the left sidebar and update the :guilabel:`Label` field "
"with a title for the new |AI| field. Then click :guilabel:`Close` to exit "
"**Studio**."
msgstr ""
"Når prompten er færdig, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Tilføj felt`. Før du "
"lukker **Studio**, skal du klikke på venstre sidepanel og opdatere "
"feltet :guilabel:`Etiket` med en titel til det nye |AI|-felt. Klik derefter "
"på :guilabel:`Luk` for at afslutte **Studio**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:65
msgid ""
"After the field is added, click the |AI| icon to refresh the field value."
msgstr ""
"Når feltet er tilføjet, skal du klikke på ikonet |AI| for at opdatere "
"feltværdien."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:68
msgid ""
"If the |AI| is unable to complete the request, a warning message is "
"generated. This could mean that the prompt is asking for information that is "
"not available, in the given context, or that the prompt is providing unclear "
"instructions. Use this as an indication to revisit the prompt and add "
"additional context or instructions."
msgstr ""
"Hvis |AI| ikke kan fuldføre anmodningen, genereres en advarselsmeddelelse. "
"Dette kan betyde, at prompten beder om information, der ikke er tilgængelig "
"i den givne kontekst, eller at prompten giver uklare instruktioner. Brug "
"dette som en indikation af, at du skal genbesøge prompten og tilføje "
"yderligere kontekst eller instruktioner."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:0
msgid "A warning message indicating the AI was unable to complete the request."
msgstr ""
"En advarselsmeddelelse, der indikerer, at KI'en ikke kunne fuldføre "
"anmodningen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:79
msgid "Add via edit properties"
msgstr "Tilføj via rediger egenskaber"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:81
msgid ""
"|AI| fields can also be added as property fields without opening the "
"**Studio** app. Click on the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions` icon and "
"select :icon:`fa-cogs` :guilabel:`Edit Properties`. Tick the :guilabel:`AI` "
"checkbox, confirm the field should be |AI|-enabled, then follow the "
"steps :ref:`above <ai/add-a-new-field>` to define the field type and enter "
"the prompt."
msgstr ""
"|AI|-felter kan også tilføjes som egenskabsfelter uden at åbne **Studio**-"
"appen. Klik på ikonet :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Handlinger`, og "
"vælg :icon:`fa-cogs` :guilabel:`Rediger egenskaber`. Markér "
"afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`KI`, bekræft at feltet skal være |AI|-"
"aktiveret, og følg derefter trinene :ref:`ovenfor <ai/add-a-new-field>` for "
"at definere felttypen og indtaste prompten."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:None
msgid "The edit properties pop-up on a form view."
msgstr "Pop-up til redigering af egenskaber på en formularvisning."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:90
msgid ""
":ref:`Property fields <property_field/add>` can only be added to form views."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Egenskabsfelter <property_field/add>` kan kun tilføjes til "
"formularvisninger."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:93
msgid "Computing AI fields"
msgstr "Beregning af KI-felter"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:95
msgid ""
"To compute, or refresh, an |AI| field, click on the |AI| icon next to the "
"field. Clicking the button updates the field based on the prompt."
msgstr ""
"For at beregne eller opdatere et |AI|-felt skal du klikke på ikonet |AI| ved "
"siden af feltet. Klik på knappen opdaterer feltet baseret på prompten."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:98
msgid ""
"Additionally, a scheduled action runs once a day to fill text and property |"
"AI| fields that are currently empty. This action is active by default."
msgstr ""
"Derudover kører en planlagt handling en gang dagligt for at udfylde tekst- "
"og egenskabs-|AI|-felter, der i øjeblikket er tomme. Denne handling er aktiv "
"som standard."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:102
msgid ""
"To run the scheduled action manually, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings "
"app --> Technical --> Automation --> Scheduled Actions`. Click "
"on :guilabel:`AI Fields\\:\\ Compute AI fields` to open it, then "
"click :guilabel:`Run Manually`."
msgstr ""
"For at køre den planlagte handling manuelt skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Indstillinger-app --> Teknisk --> Automatisering --> "
"Planlagte handlinger`. Klik på :guilabel:`KI-felter\\:\\ Beregn KI-felter` "
"for at åbne den, og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Kør manuelt`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:3
msgid "Write and improve text with AI"
msgstr "Skriv og forbedr tekst med KI"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo |AI| can assist with writing and refining text across the database. "
"This makes it easier to draft emails, improve existing content, and quickly "
"extract key information from discussions or notes."
msgstr ""
"Odoo |AI| kan hjælpe med at skrive og forfine tekst på tværs af databasen. "
"Dette gør det lettere at udarbejde e-mails, forbedre eksisterende indhold og "
"hurtigt udtrække nøgleinformation fra diskussioner eller noter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:11
msgid ""
"|AI| writing features are available in most rich-text environments in Odoo, "
"including:"
msgstr ""
"|AI|-skriveværktøjer er tilgængelige i de fleste redigeringsmiljøer i Odoo, "
"herunder:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:13
msgid "*Description* and *Notes* fields on records"
msgstr "*Beskrivelse*- og *Noter*-felter på poster"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:14
msgid "Email composers and email templates"
msgstr "Mailforfattere og mailskabeloner"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:15
msgid "**Knowledge** articles"
msgstr "**Viden**-artikler"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:17
msgid ""
"These features are accessible through the text editor and the :ref:`powerbox "
"<essentials/html_editor/commands>`, depending on the context."
msgstr ""
"Disse funktioner er tilgængelige via teksteditoren og :ref:`powerbox "
"<essentials/html_editor/commands>`, afhængigt af konteksten."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:None
msgid "A knowledge article with the AI improve text option visible."
msgstr "En Viden-artikel med KI-muligheden for at forbedre tekst synlig."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:24
msgid "Writing with AI"
msgstr "Skrivning med KI"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:26
msgid ""
"|AI| can generate new text based on a short prompt or partial input. This is "
"useful for drafting content such as emails, task descriptions, or internal "
"notes."
msgstr ""
"|AI| kan generere ny tekst baseret på en kort prompt eller delvist input. "
"Dette er nyttigt til at udarbejde indhold som e-mails, opgavebeskrivelser "
"eller interne noter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:29
msgid ""
"To generate text, either click the |AI| icon, or type `/` to open the "
"powerbox, and select :guilabel:`AI` from the drop-down menu. Both options "
"open a conversation window. Enter a short prompt describing the desired "
"content, then click the :icon:`fa-paper-plane-o` :guilabel:`(paper plane)` "
"icon. After the text is generated, hover over the response and "
"click :guilabel:`Use this` to add the content to the desired field or "
"document. Alternatively, click the :icon:`fa-copy` :guilabel:`(copy)` icon "
"to copy the text to the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"For at generere tekst skal du enten klikke på |AI|-ikonet eller trykke på `/"
"` for at åbne powerbox og vælge :guilabel:`KI` fra rullelisten. Begge "
"muligheder åbner et samtalevindue. Indtast en kort prompt, der beskriver det "
"ønskede indhold, og klik derefter på :icon:`fa-paper-plane-"
"o` :guilabel:`(papirfly)`-ikonet. Efter teksten er genereret, skal du holde "
"musen over svaret og klikke på :guilabel:`Brug dette` for at tilføje "
"indholdet til det ønskede felt eller dokument. Alternativt kan du klikke "
"på :icon:`fa-copy` :guilabel:`(kopiér)`-ikonet for at kopiere teksten til "
"udklipsholderen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:None
msgid "A conversation window with an AI agent generating content."
msgstr "Et samtalevindue med en KI-agent, der genererer indhold."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:39
msgid ""
"If unsatisfied with the content, send a follow-up message to the agent with "
"an expanded prompt or suggested changes."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du er utilfreds med indholdet, kan du sende en opfølgningsbesked til "
"agenten med en udvidet prompt eller foreslåede ændringer."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:43
msgid "Improving existing text"
msgstr "Forbedring af eksisterende tekst"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:45
msgid ""
"|AI| can also be used to rewrite or improve existing text. This includes:"
msgstr ""
"|AI| kan også bruges til at omskrive eller forbedre eksisterende tekst. "
"Dette inkluderer:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:47
msgid "Making text clearer or more concise"
msgstr "Gøre teksten klarere eller mere kortfattet"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:48
msgid "Adjusting tone or structure"
msgstr "Justere tone eller struktur"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:49
msgid "Correcting grammar or phrasing"
msgstr "Rette grammatik eller formulering"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:51
msgid ""
"Select the text to improve, then click the |AI| icon to open a conversation "
"window. Click the :guilabel:`Rewrite selected` prompt. After the text is "
"generated, hover over the response and click :guilabel:`Use this` to add the "
"content to the desired field or document. Alternatively, click the :icon:`fa-"
"copy` :guilabel:`(copy)` icon to copy the text to the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Marker teksten, der skal forbedres, og klik derefter på |AI|-ikonet for at "
"åbne et samtalevindue. Klik på prompten :guilabel:`Omskriv markeret`. Når "
"teksten er genereret, skal du holde markøren over svaret og klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Brug denne` for at tilføje indholdet til det ønskede felt "
"eller dokument. Alternativt kan du klikke på ikonet :icon:`fa-"
"copy` :guilabel:`(kopier)` for at kopiere teksten til udklipsholderen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:None
msgid "The rewrite selected text in a conversation window."
msgstr "Den omskrevne markerede tekst i et samtalevindue."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:60
msgid ""
"To add custom instructions to the prompt, such as suggestions on tone or "
"content, write the prompt directly in the conversation window. For example, "
"`Rewrite the selected text in a more professional tone`."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje brugerdefinerede instruktioner til prompten, såsom forslag "
"til tone eller indhold, skal du skrive prompten direkte i samtalevinduet. "
"For eksempel 'Omskriv den markerede tekst i en mere professionel tone'."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:65
msgid "Best practices for AI-assisted writing"
msgstr "Bedste praksis for KI-assisteret skrivning"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:67
msgid "For best results when using |AI| to write or improve text:"
msgstr ""
"For de bedste resultater, når du bruger |AI| til at skrive eller forbedre "
"tekst:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:69
msgid "Provide clear and specific context in prompts"
msgstr "Giv klar og specifik kontekst i prompts"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:70
msgid "Review AI-generated content before saving or sending"
msgstr "Gennemgå KI-genereret indhold, før du gemmer eller sender"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:71
msgid "Adjust wording to match the company's tone and communication standards"
msgstr ""
"Juster ordlyden, så den matcher virksomhedens tone og "
"kommunikationsstandarder"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:73
msgid ""
"|AI|-assisted writing is designed to support productivity, while final "
"review and validation remain essential."
msgstr ""
"|AI|-assisteret skrivning er designet til at understøtte produktiviteten, "
"mens endelig gennemgang og validering forbliver essentiel."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:3
msgid "AI live chat"
msgstr "KI live chat"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo's **AI** application can be integrated with **Live Chat** to enable "
"agents to automatically respond to customer inquiries, qualify "
"conversations, and generate leads. When connected to a live chat channel, an "
"AI agent can answer common questions, request additional information, and "
"determine when a conversation needs to be escalated to a human operator."
msgstr ""
"Odoos **KI**-applikation kan integreres med **Live Chat** for at gøre det "
"muligt for agenter automatisk at svare på kundehenvendelser, kvalificere "
"samtaler og generere leads. Når den er forbundet til en live chat-kanal, kan "
"en KI-agent besvare almindelige spørgsmål, anmode om yderligere oplysninger "
"og afgøre, hvornår en samtale skal eskaleres til en menneskelig operatør."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:10
msgid ""
"AI responses are generated in real-time and follow the rules and "
"instructions defined in the assigned agent and topics."
msgstr ""
"KI-svar genereres i realtid og følger de regler og instruktioner, der er "
"defineret i den tildelte agent og emner."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:14
msgid "Connecting an agent to live chat"
msgstr "Forbinde en agent til live chat"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:16
msgid ""
"First, confirm that both the **Live Chat** and **AI** applications are "
"installed."
msgstr ""
"Bekræft først, at både **Live Chat**- og **KI**-applikationerne er "
"installeret."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:19
msgid ""
"When both the **AI** and **Live Chat** apps are installed, a *Livechat AI "
"Agent* is added to the **AI** app. Other agents can be created and used for "
"live chat conversations, if desired."
msgstr ""
"Når både **KI**- og **Live Chat**-appene er installeret, tilføjes en "
"*Livechat AI Agent* til **KI**-appen. Andre agenter kan oprettes og bruges "
"til live chat-samtaler, hvis ønsket."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:0
msgid "The preconfigured AI Live Chat agent in the AI app."
msgstr "Den prækonfigurerede KI Live Chat-agent i KI-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:25
msgid ""
"Navigate to the **Live Chat** application and select a live chat channel. On "
"the channel card, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical "
"ellipsis)` icon, then click :guilabel:`Configure Channel`."
msgstr ""
"Naviger til **Live Chat**-applikationen og vælg en live chat-kanal. På "
"kanalkortet skal du klikke på ikonet :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`lodret "
"ellipse` og derefter klikke på :guilabel:`Konfigurer kanal`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:29
msgid ""
"On the channel page, click on the :guilabel:`Rules` tab. Click on an "
"existing rule, or click :guilabel:`Add a line` to add a new rule. On the "
"*Open: Rules* pop-up, click in the :guilabel:`AI Agent` field, and select an "
"agent from the drop-down."
msgstr ""
"På kanalsiden skal du klikke på fanen :guilabel:`Regler`. Klik på en "
"eksisterende regel, eller klik på :guilabel:`Tilføj en linje` for at tilføje "
"en ny regel. I pop op-vinduet *Åbn: Regler* skal du klikke i "
"feltet :guilabel:`KI-agent` og vælge en agent fra rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:None
msgid "The rules pop-up window in the live chat app."
msgstr "Pop op-vinduet med regler i live chat-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:37
msgid ""
"If a channel has both a chatbot and an AI Agent assigned, the priority is "
"given to the AI agent workflow."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en kanal har både en chatbot og en KI-agent tilknyttet, prioriteres KI-"
"agentens workflow."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:41
msgid "Configuring AI behavior in live chat"
msgstr "Konfigurer KI-adfærd i Live Chat"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:43
msgid ""
"The behavior and actions of the AI agent during a live chat conversation are "
"controlled through the agent's settings.  To configure the :doc:`agent "
"<agents>`, navigate to the :menuselection:`AI app --> Agents`. On the agent "
"card, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon, "
"then click :guilabel:`Configuration`."
msgstr ""
"KI-agentens adfærd og handlinger under en Live Chat-samtale styres gennem "
"agentens indstillinger. For at konfigurere :doc:`agenten <agents>`, naviger "
"til :menuselection:`KI-app --> Agenter`. På agentkortet klik på :icon:`fa-"
"ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(lodret ellipse)`-ikonet og klik derefter "
"på :guilabel:`Konfiguration`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:48
msgid ""
"As the default *Livechat AI Agent* is configured to work with live chat, "
"this section lays out how the agent's prompt is used in a live chat "
"conversation."
msgstr ""
"Da standard *Livechat AI Agent* er konfigureret til at arbejde med Live "
"Chat, beskriver dette afsnit, hvordan agentens prompt bruges i en Live Chat-"
"samtale."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:52
msgid "Agent identity and goals"
msgstr "Agentens identitet og mål"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:54
msgid ""
"The *Livechat AI Agent* identity helps define the agent's communication "
"style and conversation goals. At a high level, the agent is focused on "
"answering customer questions accurately, while also being responsible for "
"initiating lead creation when a request cannot be handled confidently."
msgstr ""
"*Livechat AI Agent*-identiteten hjælper med at definere agentens "
"kommunikationsstil og samtalemål. På et overordnet niveau fokuserer agenten "
"på at besvare kundespørgsmål præcist, samtidig med at den er ansvarlig for "
"at igangsætte leadoprettelse, når en anmodning ikke kan håndteres med "
"sikkerhed."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:58
msgid ""
"Rather than reacting message-by-message, the agent evaluates each "
"interaction against its defined priorities."
msgstr ""
"I stedet for at reagere besked-for-besked evaluerer agenten hver interaktion "
"i forhold til sine definerede prioriteter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:62
msgid "How the agent answers questions"
msgstr "Hvordan agenten besvarer spørgsmål"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:64
msgid ""
"During a conversation, each incoming message is evaluated against the "
"agent's decision rules. When sufficient information is available, the agent "
"responds directly with a clear and concise answer."
msgstr ""
"Under en samtale evalueres hver indgående besked i forhold til agentens "
"beslutningsregler. Når der er tilstrækkelig information tilgængelig, svarer "
"agenten direkte med et klart og præcist svar."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:67
msgid ""
"If the available information is incomplete or uncertain, the agent does not "
"guess or fabricate a response. Instead, it acknowledges the limitation and "
"prepares to transition the conversation toward human follow-up."
msgstr ""
"Hvis den tilgængelige information er ufuldstændig eller usikker, gætter "
"eller opfinder agenten ikke et svar. I stedet anerkender den begrænsningen "
"og forbereder at overføre samtalen til menneskelig opfølgning."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:71
msgid "This ensures that automated responses remain accurate and trustworthy."
msgstr ""
"Dette sikrer, at automatiserede svar forbliver nøjagtige og troværdige."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:74
msgid "How escalation is triggered"
msgstr "Hvordan eskalering udløses"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:76
msgid ""
"Escalation to human follow-up is defined explicitly in the agent's prompt "
"and delegated to a dedicated topic."
msgstr ""
"Eskalering til menneskelig opfølgning er defineret eksplicit i agentens "
"prompt og delegeret til et dedikeret emne."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:79
msgid "Conversations are escalated when one of the following occurs:"
msgstr "Samtaler eskaleres, når en af følgende situationer opstår:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:81
msgid "The request requires custom pricing, contracts, or implementation work."
msgstr ""
"Anmodningen kræver tilpasset prissætning, kontrakter eller "
"implementeringsarbejde."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:82
msgid "The request involves account changes or troubleshooting."
msgstr "Anmodningen involverer kontoændringer eller fejlfinding."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:83
msgid "The user explicitly asks to be contacted or requests a demo."
msgstr ""
"Brugeren beder eksplicit om at blive kontaktet eller anmoder om en demo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:84
msgid "The agent cannot respond with high confidence."
msgstr "Agenten kan ikke svare med høj tillid."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:86
msgid ""
"When one of these conditions is met, the agent activates the *Lead "
"Creation* :ref:`topic <ai/topics>`."
msgstr ""
"Når en af disse betingelser er opfyldt, aktiverer agenten :ref:`emnet <ai/"
"topics>` *Lead Creation*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:90
msgid "Lead creation topic"
msgstr "Lead creation-emne"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:92
msgid ""
"The Lead creation topic defines a structured, multi-step workflow that "
"governs how contact information is collected and how a lead is created."
msgstr ""
"Emnet for leadoprettelse definerer en struktureret arbejdsgang i flere trin, "
"der styrer, hvordan kontaktoplysninger indsamles, og hvordan et lead "
"oprettes."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:95
msgid "This topic specifies:"
msgstr "Dette emne specificerer:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:97
msgid "when lead creation is appropriate"
msgstr "hvornår leadoprettelse er hensigtsmæssig"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:98
msgid "what information must be collected"
msgstr "hvilke oplysninger der skal indsamles"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:99
msgid "how the conversation should progress"
msgstr "hvordan samtalen skal forløbe"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:100
msgid "what language the agent may and may not use"
msgstr "hvilket sprog agenten må og ikke må bruge"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:102
msgid ""
"Rather than immediately creating a lead, the agent completes the following "
"steps:"
msgstr ""
"I stedet for straks at oprette et lead gennemfører agenten følgende trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:104
msgid "Suggests human follow-up when appropriate"
msgstr "Foreslår personlig opfølgning, når det er relevant"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:105
msgid "Collects missing contact details one at a time"
msgstr "Indsamler manglende kontaktoplysninger én ad gangen"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:106
msgid "Confirms known details before proceeding"
msgstr "Bekræfter kendte detaljer, før der fortsættes"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:107
msgid "Calls the lead creation tool exactly once"
msgstr "Kalder leadoprettelsesværktøjet præcis én gang"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:109
msgid ""
"The topic also enforces strict constraints to prevent system-centric "
"language, duplicate lead creation, or premature promises of follow-up."
msgstr ""
"Emnet håndhæver også strenge begrænsninger for at forhindre systemcentreret "
"sprog, duplikeret leadoprettelse eller for tidlige løfter om opfølgning."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:112
msgid ""
"To view the detailed instructions for the lead creation topic, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`AI app --> Agents --> Topics`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Create Leads`."
msgstr ""
"For at se de detaljerede instruktioner for leadoprettelsesemnet skal du "
"navigere til :menuselection:`KI-app --> Agenter --> Emner` og klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Opret leads`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:116
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:133
msgid ":doc:`AI Agents <agents>`"
msgstr ":doc:`KI-agenter <agents>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:3
msgid "AI server actions"
msgstr "KI-serverhandlinger"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:7
msgid ""
"|AI| server actions extend Odoo's automation framework by allowing "
"artificial intelligence to make decisions during a workflow."
msgstr ""
"|AI|-serverhandlinger udvider Odoos automationsramme ved at tillade kunstig "
"intelligens at træffe beslutninger under et workflow."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:10
msgid ""
"They are designed for cases where logic cannot be expressed entirely through "
"fixed conditions, but still requires controlled execution through standard "
"server actions."
msgstr ""
"De er designet til situationer, hvor logik ikke kan udtrykkes fuldstændigt "
"gennem faste betingelser, men stadig kræver kontrolleret udførelse gennem "
"standardserverhandlinger."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:14
msgid "How AI server actions work"
msgstr "Sådan fungerer KI-serverhandlinger"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:16
msgid ""
"AI-driven workflows in Odoo are built around a clear separation of "
"responsibilities between the |AI| server action, or *the Manager*, and the "
"tool, or *the Worker*."
msgstr ""
"KI-drevne workflows i Odoo er bygget omkring en klar ansvarsfordeling mellem "
"|AI|-serverhandlingen, eller *manageren*, og værktøjet, eller *workeren*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:20
msgid "AI server action: the manager"
msgstr "KI-serverhandling: manageren"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:22
msgid ""
"An |AI| server action acts as a decision maker, or a manager. It reads the "
"record and its context. It interprets the |AI| prompt. And it decides which "
"tool to call, and what arguments to use."
msgstr ""
"En |AI|-serverhandling fungerer som beslutningstageren eller en manager. Den "
"læser posten og dens kontekst. Den fortolker |AI|-prompten. Og den "
"beslutter, hvilket værktøj der skal kaldes, og hvilke argumenter der skal "
"bruges."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:25
msgid ""
"The server action does not enforce business rules, modify records directly, "
"or guarantee the correctness of the operation. Its role is limited to "
"decision-making."
msgstr ""
"Serverhandlingen håndhæver ikke forretningsregler, ændrer ikke poster "
"direkte og garanterer ikke operationens korrekthed. Dens rolle er begrænset "
"til beslutningstagning."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:29
msgid "AI tool: the worker"
msgstr "KI-værktøj: workeren"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:31
msgid ""
"A tool is a standard server action with the *Use in AI* option enabled in "
"its *Usage* tab. Tools contain all execution logic and perform record "
"updates, moves, or writes. Tools **must** enforce business rules explicitly "
"in Python code."
msgstr ""
"Et værktøj er en standardserverhandling med muligheden *Brug i KI* aktiveret "
"under fanen *Anvendelse*. Værktøjer indeholder al udførelseslogik og udfører "
"postopdateringer, flytninger eller skrivninger. Værktøjer **skal** håndhæve "
"forretningsregler eksplicit i Python-kode."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:35
msgid ""
"If a tool is called by the |AI| server action, it will execute "
"unconditionally, unless the code itself prevents it."
msgstr ""
"Hvis et værktøj kaldes af |AI|-serverhandlingen, vil det udføres ubetinget, "
"medmindre koden selv forhindrer det."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:39
msgid "AI server action workflow"
msgstr "KI-serverhandlingsworkflow"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:41
msgid "The |AI| server action workflow follows this sequence:"
msgstr "|AI|-serverhandlingsworkflowet følger denne sekvens:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:43
msgid "A record triggers an |AI| server action."
msgstr "En post udløser en |AI|-serverhandling."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:44
msgid "The |AI| prompt is evaluated, using the record as context."
msgstr "|AI|-prompten evalueres ved at bruge posten som kontekst."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:45
msgid "The |AI| selects one of the available tools."
msgstr "|AI| vælger et af de tilgængelige værktøjer."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:46
msgid "The |AI| provides arguments expected by the tool."
msgstr "|AI| leverer de argumenter, værktøjet forventer."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:47
msgid "The selected tool executes its Python code."
msgstr "Det valgte værktøj udfører sin Python-kode."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:50
msgid ""
"|AI| server actions work without custom logic only when the underlying "
"behavior already exists in Odoo, such as moving a document to a folder. In "
"these cases, the |AI| selects parameters, and Odoo executes the action."
msgstr ""
"|AI|-serverhandlinger fungerer uden brugerdefineret logik kun, når den "
"underliggende adfærd allerede findes i Odoo, såsom at flytte et dokument til "
"en mappe. I disse tilfælde vælger |AI| parametre, og Odoo udfører handlingen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:55
msgid "Use case walkthrough"
msgstr "Gennemgang af use case"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:57
msgid ""
"The *Auto-sort documents in Inbox* example demonstrates the full |AI| Server "
"Action pattern. Navigate to the *Server Actions* menu by going "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> Server Actions`."
msgstr ""
"Eksemplet *Auto-sort documents in Inbox* demonstrerer det fulde |AI|-"
"serverhandlingsmønster. Naviger til menuen *Serverhandlinger* ved at gå "
"til :menuselection:`Indstillinger --> Teknisk --> Serverhandlinger`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:62
msgid ""
"This server action is designed to review documents for their content, and "
"add tags. The action itself does **not** move documents or add tags, it only "
"decides which tool should be used, based on the documents' content."
msgstr ""
"Denne serverhandling er designet til at gennemgå dokumenter for deres "
"indhold og tilføje tags. Selve handlingen flytter **ikke** dokumenter eller "
"tilføjer tags, den beslutter kun, hvilket værktøj der skal bruges, baseret "
"på dokumenternes indhold."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:66
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Model` for the action is listed as *Document*, and "
"the :guilabel:`Type` is *AI*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Modellen` for handlingen er angivet som *Dokument*, "
"og :guilabel:`typen` er *KI*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:None
msgid "The record for the Auto-sort documents in inbox server action."
msgstr "Posten for serverhandlingen Auto-sort documents in inbox."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:71
msgid ""
"The prompt for this action provides context about the document, as well as "
"intent of the action."
msgstr ""
"Prompten for denne handling giver kontekst om dokumentet samt formålet med "
"handlingen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:73
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Tool` field includes several actions that may be taken based "
"on this prompt, including moving a document, adding tags, or creating "
"invoices or bills."
msgstr ""
"Feltet :guilabel:`Værktøj` omfatter flere handlinger, der kan udføres "
"baseret på denne prompt, herunder flytning af et dokument, tilføjelse af "
"tags eller oprettelse af fakturaer eller regninger."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:77
msgid ""
"*AI: Add Tags*, *AI: Move to Folder*, and *AI: Rename Document* are all "
"*Execute Code* server actions, meaning they trigger python code."
msgstr ""
"*AI: Add Tags*, *AI: Move to Folder* og *AI: Rename Document* er alle *Udfør "
"kode*-serverhandlinger, hvilket betyder, at de udløser Python-kode."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:80
msgid ""
"For example, if the action determines, based on the content of the document, "
"that the most appropriate tool is *AI: Move to Folder*, the Python code "
"performs the following operation:"
msgstr ""
"Hvis handlingen f.eks. bestemmer ud fra dokumentets indhold, at det mest "
"passende værktøj er *AI: Move to Folder*, udfører Python-koden følgende "
"operation:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:87
msgid ""
"This code, executes unconditionally when called and performs the move using "
"an existing method."
msgstr ""
"Denne kode udføres ubetinget, når den kaldes, og udfører flytningen ved "
"hjælp af en eksisterende metode."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:90
msgid ""
"The |AI| does not infer arguments from the Python code or from the method "
"signature. Instead, arguments passed to a tool are determined entirely by "
"the tool's configuration."
msgstr ""
"|AI| udleder ikke argumenter fra Python-koden eller fra metodesignaturen. I "
"stedet bestemmes argumenter, der sendes til et værktøj, udelukkende af "
"værktøjets konfiguration."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:93
msgid ""
"For the *AI: Move to Folder* tool, the Python code expects a variable named "
"`folder_id`. The |AI| knows to provide `folder_id` because it is explicitly "
"declared as an argument in the configuration. This can be found on the "
"*Usage* tab of the server action, in the :guilabel:`AI Schema` field. "
"The :guilabel:`Name` column under *AI Schema* must match the variable name "
"used in the Python code exactly."
msgstr ""
"Pro nástroj *AI: Přesunout do složky* očekává kód Pythonu proměnnou s názvem "
"`folder_id`. |AI| ví, že má poskytnout `folder_id`, protože je explicitně "
"deklarována jako argument v konfiguraci. Toto lze nalézt na kartě *Použití* "
"serverové akce v poli :guilabel:`AI Schema`. Sloupec :guilabel:`Název` pod "
"*AI Schema* se musí přesně shodovat s názvem proměnné použité v kódu Pythonu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:99
msgid ""
"The |AI| uses the argument description to understand what the parameter "
"represents, what type of value is expected, and when it is appropriate to "
"supply it."
msgstr ""
"|AI| používá popis argumentu k pochopení, co parametr představuje, jaký typ "
"hodnoty se očekává a kdy je vhodné jej poskytnout."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:102
msgid ""
"If an argument is not defined in the Usage tab, the AI cannot provide it, "
"even if the Python code references it."
msgstr ""
"Pokud argument není definován na kartě Použití, KI jej nemůže poskytnout, i "
"když na něj odkazuje kód Pythonu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:0
msgid "The usage tab of the AI move to folder server action."
msgstr "Karta použití serverové akce AI přesunout do složky."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:109
msgid "Creating custom AI tools"
msgstr "Vytváření vlastních nástrojů KI"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:111
msgid ""
"The same pattern in the *Auto-sort documents in Inbox* example above can be "
"implemented using standard Odoo logic. For example, to create an action that "
"can update a task description, an *Execute Code* action could be created "
"with the following code:"
msgstr ""
"Stejný vzor v příkladu *Automatické třídění dokumentů ve Schránce* výše lze "
"implementovat pomocí standardní logiky Odoo. Například pro vytvoření akce, "
"která může aktualizovat popis úkolu, by mohla být vytvořena akce *Spustit "
"kód* s následujícím kódem:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:119
msgid ""
"To function correctly, `content` **must** be defined as an argument in "
"tool's *Usage* tab."
msgstr ""
"Aby správně fungovala, `content` **musí** být definována jako argument na "
"kartě *Použití* nástroje."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:122
msgid ":ref:`Server Actions <reference/actions/server>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Serverové akce <reference/actions/server>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:125
msgid "Common issues"
msgstr "Běžné problémy"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:128
msgid "Why is the Tools field empty?"
msgstr "Proč je pole Nástroje prázdné?"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:130
msgid ""
"Confirm that at least one server action has :guilabel:`Use in AI` enabled."
msgstr ""
"Potvrďte, že alespoň jedna serverová akce má povoleno :guilabel:`Použít v "
"AI`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:131
msgid ""
"Confirm that at least one tool is assigned to the same "
"model :guilabel:`Model` as the server action."
msgstr ""
"Potvrďte, že alespoň jeden nástroj je přiřazen ke stejnému "
"modelu :guilabel:`Model` jako serverová akce."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:135
msgid "Why did the tool run but nothing happened?"
msgstr "Proč se nástroj spustil, ale nic se nestalo?"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:137
msgid "The Python code exited without changes."
msgstr "Kód Pythonu skončil bez změn."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:138
msgid "Required arguments were missing or empty."
msgstr "Požadované argumenty chyběly nebo byly prázdné."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:139
msgid "Business conditions were not implemented in the tool logic."
msgstr "Obchodní podmínky nebyly implementovány v logice nástroje."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:142
msgid "Why did the AI choose an unexpected tool?"
msgstr "Proč KI vybrala neočekávaný nástroj?"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:144
msgid "The prompt lacked sufficient context."
msgstr "Výzvě chyběl dostatečný kontext."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:145
msgid "Multiple tools matched the same intent."
msgstr "Více nástrojů odpovídalo stejnému záměru."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:146
msgid "No constraints were enforced at the tool level."
msgstr "Na úrovni nástroje nebyla vynucena žádná omezení."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:3
msgid "AI in support workflows"
msgstr "KI i supportarbejdsgange"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:7
msgid ""
"Utilizing Odoo's |AI| features in the **Helpdesk** app assists support "
"agents with their tasks, rather than replacing existing workflows. The goal "
"is to reduce repetitive tasks, accelerate ticket handling, and improve "
"consistency by allowing |AI| to analyze ticket content and suggest or "
"execute actions automatically."
msgstr ""
"Brug af Odoos |AI| funktioner i **Kundeservice**-appen hjælper "
"supportagenter med deres opgaver i stedet for at erstatte eksisterende "
"arbejdsgange. Målet er at reducere gentagne opgaver, fremskynde ticket-"
"håndtering og forbedre konsistens ved at tillade |AI| at analysere ticket-"
"indhold og foreslå eller udføre handlinger automatisk."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:12
msgid ""
"Instead of manually categorizing, prioritizing, and responding to every "
"request, support teams can rely on |AI| to interpret incoming information "
"and perform preliminary processing. Agents remain in control of decisions "
"and customer communication, while |AI| handles repetitive analysis and "
"drafting."
msgstr ""
"Namísto ručního kategorizování, stanovování priorit a odpovídání na každý "
"požadavek se týmy podpory mohou spolehnout na |AI|, který interpretuje "
"příchozí informace a provádí předběžné zpracování. Agenti mají kontrolu nad "
"rozhodnutími a komunikací se zákazníky, zatímco |AI| se stará o opakující se "
"analýzy a návrhy."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:18
msgid "How AI works in Helpdesk"
msgstr "Jak AI funguje v Kundeservice"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:20
msgid "|AI| capabilities in **Helpdesk** are built around three core ideas:"
msgstr ""
"|AI| funkce v **Kundeservice** jsou postaveny na třech základních myšlenkách:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:22
msgid ""
"|AI| agents that interact with users or agents and generate responses based "
"on knowledge sources."
msgstr ""
"|AI| agenti, kteří komunikují s uživateli nebo agenty a generují odpovědi na "
"základě znalostních zdrojů."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:23
msgid ""
"|AI| automations that update tickets automatically when records are created "
"or modified."
msgstr ""
"|AI| automatizace, které aktualizují tikety automaticky při vytvoření nebo "
"úpravě záznamů."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:24
msgid ""
"|AI| enabled fields that generate structured information, such as summaries, "
"from unstructured text."
msgstr ""
"|AI| povolená pole, která generují strukturované informace, jako jsou "
"shrnutí, z nestrukturovaného textu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:30
msgid ""
"An |AI| agent is a configurable assistant that operates using prompts and "
"contextual knowledge. The agent itself does not contain business logic; "
"instead, it follows instructions defined by users and relies on provided "
"documentation."
msgstr ""
"|AI| agent je konfigurovatelný asistent, který pracuje pomocí promptů a "
"kontextových znalostí. Agent sám neobsahuje obchodní logiku, místo toho se "
"řídí pokyny definovanými uživateli a spoléhá na poskytnutou dokumentaci."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:34
msgid ""
"When an agent receives a request, it combines its system :ref:`prompt <ai/"
"agents/prompts-in-odoo>`, the current record context (such as a ticket), and "
"its knowledge :ref:`sources <ai/sources>`."
msgstr ""
"Když agent obdrží požadavek, kombinuje svůj systémový :ref:`prompt <ai/"
"agents/prompts-in-odoo>`, kontext aktuálního záznamu (jako je tiket) a své "
"znalostní :ref:`zdroje <ai/sources>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:37
msgid ""
"This allows the agent to provide responses grounded in internal "
"documentation rather than generic language model output."
msgstr ""
"To umožňuje agentovi poskytovat odpovědi založené na interní dokumentaci "
"namísto generického výstupu jazykového modelu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:40
msgid ""
"Agents can be restricted to specific sources or granted permissions to "
"perform actions using topics. This ensures that support assistants behave "
"predictably and remain aligned with organizational rules."
msgstr ""
"Agenti mohou být omezeni na konkrétní zdroje nebo jim mohou být udělena "
"oprávnění k provádění akcí pomocí témat. To zajišťuje, že asistenti podpory "
"se chovají předvídatelně a zůstávají v souladu s organizačními pravidly."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:45
msgid "AI automations"
msgstr "Automatizace AI"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:47
msgid ""
"Automation rules allow |AI| to act during record lifecycle events. Instead "
"of waiting for an agent to categorize or prioritize tickets, |AI| can "
"perform these tasks automatically as soon as a ticket is created."
msgstr ""
"Pravidla automatizace umožňují |AI| jednat během událostí životního cyklu "
"záznamu. Namísto čekání na to, až agent kategorizuje nebo určí prioritu "
"tiketů, může |AI| tyto úkoly provádět automaticky ihned po vytvoření tiketu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:51
msgid ""
"The key principle is that |AI| does not understand Odoo models directly. It "
"receives text extracted from fields and produces an output based on prompt "
"instructions. Users guide |AI| behavior through clear prompting and "
"carefully selected input fields."
msgstr ""
"Klíčovým principem je, že |AI| nerozumí modelům Odoo přímo. Přijímá text "
"extrahovaný z polí a vytváří výstup na základě instrukcí promptu. Uživatelé "
"řídí chování |AI| prostřednictvím jasného promptování a pečlivě vybraných "
"vstupních polí."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:58
msgid ""
"|AI| enabled fields extend standard Odoo fields by allowing their values to "
"be generated automatically through prompts."
msgstr ""
"|AI| povolená pole rozšiřují standardní pole Odoo tím, že umožňují "
"automatické generování jejich hodnot prostřednictvím promptů."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:61
msgid ""
"These fields are useful when large amounts of text need to be condensed into "
"actionable information. For example, a long customer message can "
"automatically be summarized into a short list of key points, allowing agents "
"to understand issues quickly without reading full descriptions."
msgstr ""
"Tato pole jsou užitečná, když je třeba velké množství textu zhustit do "
"použitelných informací. Například dlouhá zpráva od zákazníka může být "
"automaticky shrnuta do krátkého seznamu klíčových bodů, což agentům umožní "
"rychle porozumět problémům bez čtení úplných popisů."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:69
msgid "Configuring an AI agent for support"
msgstr "Konfigurace AI agenta pro podporu"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:71
msgid ""
"|AI| :doc:`agents <agents>` are configured in the **AI** application. To "
"configure an existing agent, navigate to :menuselection:`AI app` and click "
"the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon, then "
"click :guilabel:`Configuration` on the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"|AI| :doc:`agenti <agents>` jsou konfigurováni v aplikaci **AI**. Chcete-li "
"konfigurovat existujícího agenta, přejděte do :menuselection:`aplikace AI` a "
"klikněte na ikonu :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(svislé tři tečky)`, poté "
"klikněte na :guilabel:`Konfigurace` v rozbalovací nabídce."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:75
msgid ""
"Configuring begins by selecting a language model and defining a system "
"prompt describing how the agent should behave. The prompt determines tone, "
"scope, and responsibility. A support-focused agent might be instructed to "
"analyze issues and provide concise technical responses."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurace začína výběrem jazykového modelu a definováním systémového "
"promptu popisujícího, jak by se agent měl chovat. Prompt určuje tón, rozsah "
"a odpovědnost. Agent zaměřený na podporu může být instruován k analýze "
"problémů a poskytování stručných technických odpovědí."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:79
msgid ""
"The next step is defining the agent's *sources*. These :ref:`sources <ai/"
"sources>` form the agent's memory and should contain trusted documentation "
"such as product guides or FAQs. The quality of these sources directly "
"impacts the quality of AI responses."
msgstr ""
"Dalším krokem je definování *zdrojů* agenta. Tyto :ref:`zdroje <ai/sources>` "
"tvoří paměť agenta a měly by obsahovat důvěryhodnou dokumentaci, jako jsou "
"produktové příručky nebo FAQ. Kvalita těchto zdrojů přímo ovlivňuje kvalitu "
"AI odpovědí."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:84
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Restrict to Sources` to require the agent to **only** base "
"their responses on the supplied resources."
msgstr ""
"Vyberte :guilabel:`Omezit na zdroje`, abyste vyžadovali, aby agent své "
"odpovědi zakládal **pouze** na poskytnutých zdrojích."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:87
msgid ""
"Users may also define *topics*, which grant the agent permission to perform "
"specific actions. :ref:`Topics <ai/topics>` allow advanced scenarios such as "
"record creation or automation triggers."
msgstr ""
"Brugere kan også definere *emner*, som giver agenten tilladelse til at "
"udføre specifikke handlinger. :ref:`Emner <ai/topics>` muliggør avancerede "
"scenarier såsom oprettelse af poster eller automatiseringsudløsere."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:None
msgid "An example support AI agent."
msgstr "Et eksempel på en support-KI-agent."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:93
msgid ""
"Once an agent exists, *default prompts* can be used to initiate a "
"conversation."
msgstr ""
"Når en agent eksisterer, kan *standardprompter* bruges til at starte en "
"samtale."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:95
msgid ""
"A default prompt defines where and when the |AI| appears inside Odoo. In the "
"**Helpdesk** app, this typically means allowing the |AI| button to appear on "
"ticket records. The default prompt specifies the model where it is "
"available, which agent is called, and additional contextual instructions."
msgstr ""
"En standardprompt definerer, hvor og hvornår |AI| vises inde i Odoo. I appen "
"**Kundeservice** betyder dette typisk, at knappen |AI| kan vises på "
"ticketposter. Standardprompten angiver modellen, hvor den er tilgængelig, "
"hvilken agent der kaldes, og yderligere kontekstuelle instruktioner."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:None
msgid "A list of default prompts assigned to the Support Agent."
msgstr "En liste over standardprompter tildelt til support-agenten."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:102
msgid ""
"These instructions act as a second layer on top of the agent prompt, "
"adapting the agent's behavior to **Helpdesk** scenarios."
msgstr ""
"Disse instruktioner fungerer som et andet lag oven på agentprompten og "
"tilpasser agentens adfærd til **Kundeservice**-scenarier."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:106
msgid "Configuring AI automations"
msgstr "Konfigurere KI-automatiseringer"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:108
msgid ""
"|AI| :doc:`server actions <server-actions>` are configured using standard "
"automated actions, with |AI| used as the update mechanism."
msgstr ""
"|AI| :doc:`serverhandlinger <server-actions>` konfigureres ved hjælp af "
"standard automatiserede handlinger, hvor |AI| bruges som "
"opdateringsmekanisme."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:111
msgid ""
"When defining a server action, users specify when the action should run, "
"such as when a new ticket is created. The |AI| prompt then explains how the "
"ticket should be interpreted and which field should be updated."
msgstr ""
"Når der defineres en serverhandling, angiver brugere, hvornår handlingen "
"skal køre, f.eks. når en ny ticket oprettes. |AI|-prompten forklarer "
"derefter, hvordan ticketen skal fortolkes, og hvilket felt der skal "
"opdateres."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:115
msgid ""
"This approach keeps automation predictable while allowing |AI| to make "
"contextual decisions."
msgstr ""
"Denne fremgangsmåde holder automatiseringen forudsigelig, samtidig med at |"
"AI| kan træffe kontekstuelle beslutninger."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:118
msgid "Configuring AI fields"
msgstr "Konfigurere KI-felter"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:120
msgid ""
"|AI| :doc:`fields <fields>` are configured by enabling the |AI| option on a "
"custom or property field and providing a prompt describing the expected "
"result. Once configured, the field updates automatically when the record "
"changes, giving agents instant access to structured information."
msgstr ""
"|AI| :doc:`felter <fields>` konfigureres ved at aktivere |AI|-indstillingen "
"på et tilpasset felt eller egenskabsfelt og give en prompt, der beskriver "
"det forventede resultat. Når det er konfigureret, opdateres feltet "
"automatisk, når posten ændres, hvilket giver agenter øjeblikkelig adgang til "
"struktureret information."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:125
msgid ""
"|AI| fields can be added to a record through the **Studio** app or property "
"field. :ref:`Installing Studio <general/install>` may impact the current "
"pricing plan for a database."
msgstr ""
"|AI|-felter kan tilføjes til en post via appen **Studio** eller "
"egenskabsfeltet. :ref:`Installation af Studio <general/install>` kan påvirke "
"den aktuelle prisplan for en database."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:128
msgid ""
"For more information, refer to `Odoo's pricing page <https://www.odoo.com/"
"pricing-plan>`_ or contact your account manager."
msgstr ""
"For mere information, se `Odoos prisside <https://www.odoo.com/pricing-"
"plan>`_ eller kontakt din account manager."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:132
msgid ":doc:`AI Fields <fields>`"
msgstr ":doc:`KI-felter <fields>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:134
msgid ":doc:`AI Server Actions <server-actions>`"
msgstr ":doc:`KI-serverhandlinger <server-actions>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:3
msgid "AI voice transcription"
msgstr "KI-stemmetranskription"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo |AI| can transcribe spoken audio into text and generate summaries from "
"that transcript. This feature supports both meeting recordings and real-time "
"dictation, making it easier to capture notes, decisions, and action items "
"without manual typing."
msgstr ""
"Odoo |AI| kan transskribere talt lyd til tekst og generere resuméer fra "
"denne transkription. Denne funktion understøtter både mødeoptagelser og "
"diktering i realtid, hvilket gør det lettere at fastholde notater, "
"beslutninger og handlingspunkter uden manuel indtastning."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:11
msgid ""
"Voice transcription converts spoken audio into a written transcript. Once a "
"transcript is available, Odoo |AI| can generate a summary that highlights "
"key information, such as:"
msgstr ""
"Stemmetranskription konverterer talt lyd til en skriftlig transkription. Når "
"en transkription er tilgængelig, kan Odoo |AI| generere et resumé, der "
"fremhæver nøgleinformation, såsom:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:14
msgid "key discussion points"
msgstr "centrale diskussionspunkter"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:15
msgid "decisions"
msgstr "beslutninger"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:16
msgid "action items"
msgstr "handlingspunkter"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:17
msgid "next steps"
msgstr "næste skridt"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:19
msgid ""
"Transcription and summarization can be used for meetings, calls, quick "
"dictations, and internal notes."
msgstr ""
"Transkription og resumering kan bruges til møder, opkald, hurtige "
"dikteringer og interne notater."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:23
msgid ""
"Voice transcripts can be created in the *Description* and *Notes* fields of "
"most records, as well as in **Knowledge** articles."
msgstr ""
"Stemmetranskriptioner kan oprettes i felterne *Beskrivelse* og *Notater* på "
"de fleste poster samt i **Viden**-artikler."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:0
msgid "The powerbox in the description tab of a task in the Projects app."
msgstr "Powerbox'en i beskrivelsesf anen for en opgave i appen Projekter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:29
msgid ""
"Voice transcription works by temporarily recording audio during the session, "
"replaying it for transcription, and generating a written transcript and "
"summary. Once the transcription process is complete, the audio recording is "
"automatically discarded. The recorded audio is not stored, replayable, or "
"accessible from the database."
msgstr ""
"Stemmetranskription fungerer ved midlertidigt at optage lyd under sessionen, "
"afspille den til transkription og generere en skriftlig transkription og "
"resumé. Når transkriptionsprocessen er fuldført, bliver lydoptagelsen "
"automatisk kasseret. Den optagede lyd gemmes ikke, kan ikke afspilles og er "
"ikke tilgængelig fra databasen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:35
msgid "Transcribe a meeting"
msgstr "Transskribér et møde"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:37
msgid ""
"To create a voice transcript, type `/` to open the :ref:`powerbox "
"<essentials/html_editor/commands>`. Select :guilabel:`Voice Transcript` from "
"the drop-down list. This creates a new text block. Click :icon:`fa-"
"bars` :guilabel:`Notes` to add notes and details regarding the meeting. This "
"is where information, such as a meeting agenda and attendees, can be added. "
"Click :icon:`fa-microphone` :guilabel:`Transcript` to switch to a live view "
"of the transcript being created in real-time."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en stemmetranskription skal du skrive `/` for at "
"åbne :ref:`powerbox'en <essentials/html_editor/commands>`. "
"Vælg :guilabel:`Stemmetranskription` fra rullelisten. Dette opretter en ny "
"tekstblok. Klik på :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`Notater` for at tilføje "
"notater og detaljer om mødet. Her kan information såsom en mødedagsorden og "
"deltagere tilføjes. Klik på :icon:`fa-microphone` :guilabel:`Transkription` "
"for at skifte til en live-visning af transkriptionen, der oprettes i realtid."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:44
msgid ""
"When the meeting is ready to begin, click :icon:`fa-circle` :guilabel:`Start "
"Recording`."
msgstr ""
"Når mødet er klar til at begynde, skal du klikke på :icon:`fa-"
"circle` :guilabel:`Start optagelse`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:47
msgid ""
"Clicking :icon:`fa-circle` :guilabel:`Start Recording` may cause a pop-up in "
"the browser, requesting access to a microphone. If permission is not given, "
"the recording stops, and an error message appears. To combat this error, "
"refresh the page and allow Odoo access to the microphone."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du klikker på :icon:`fa-circle` :guilabel:`Start optagelse`, kan der "
"komme en pop op i browseren, der anmoder om adgang til en mikrofon. Hvis "
"tilladelse ikke gives, stopper optagelsen, og der vises en fejlmeddelelse. "
"For at løse denne fejl skal du opdatere siden og give Odoo adgang til "
"mikrofonen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:51
msgid ""
"When the meeting has ended, click :icon:`fa-stop` :guilabel:`Stop "
"Recording`. The recorded audio is then processed to generate a transcript "
"and an |AI| summary. Once processing is complete, the audio recording is "
"automatically discarded, leaving only the transcript and summary available."
msgstr ""
"Når mødet er slut, skal du klikke på :icon:`fa-stop` :guilabel:`Stop "
"optagelse`. Den optagede lyd behandles derefter for at generere en "
"transkription og et |AI|-resumé. Når behandlingen er fuldført, kasseres "
"lydoptagelsen automatisk, så kun transkriptionen og resuméet er tilgængeligt."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:None
msgid "The AI summary of a meeting transctipt."
msgstr "KI-resuméet af en mødetranskription."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:58
msgid ""
"The |AI| summary can be manually edited to provide additional insight, such "
"as identifying meeting attendees by name, or specifying key points. The "
"meeting notes can then be converted into an email recap, or shared directly "
"via email by clicking the :guilabel:`Share by email` button."
msgstr ""
"|AI|-resuméet kan redigeres manuelt for at give yderligere indsigt, såsom at "
"identificere mødedeltagere ved navn eller specificere nøglepunkter. "
"Mødenotaterne kan derefter konverteres til en e-mail-opsummering eller deles "
"direkte via e-mail ved at klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Del via e-mail`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:6
msgid "Appointments"
msgstr "Aftaler"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:8
msgid ""
"Odoo's **Appointments** app is a self-service scheduling app that simplifies "
"the process of booking meetings, consultations, or services. Integrated with "
"Odoo's suite of business apps, it allows companies to automate appointment "
"scheduling, reduce manual coordination, and provide a seamless experience "
"for clients. Appointments can be linked to calendars, **CRM** opportunities, "
"employee schedules, and more, making it an ideal tool for service-based "
"businesses seeking efficiency and organization."
msgstr ""
"Odoos **Aftaler**-app er en selvbetjeningsapp til planlægning, der forenkler "
"processen med at booke møder, konsultationer eller tjenester. Integreret med "
"Odoos pakke af forretningsapps gør den det muligt for virksomheder at "
"automatisere aftaleplanlægning, reducere manuel koordinering og give en "
"problemfri oplevelse for kunder. Aftaler kan linkes til kalendere, **CRM**-"
"muligheder, medarbejderplaner og mere, hvilket gør den til et ideelt værktøj "
"for servicebaserede virksomheder, der søger effektivitet og organisation."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:18
msgid ""
"The **Appointments** app allows for new appointments to be scheduled based "
"on the availability of users, or the availability of *resources*, such as "
"meeting rooms or seating areas. To create a new resource, or manage existing "
"resources, navigate to :menuselection:`Appointments --> Configuration --> "
"Resources`. This opens a list of the available resources in the database, as "
"well as their individual capacity."
msgstr ""
"**Aftaler**-appen gør det muligt at planlægge nye aftaler baseret på "
"tilgængeligheden af brugere eller tilgængeligheden af *ressourcer*, såsom "
"mødelokaler eller siddeområder. For at oprette en ny ressource eller "
"administrere eksisterende ressourcer skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Aftaler --> Konfiguration --> Ressourcer`. Dette åbner "
"en liste over de tilgængelige ressourcer i databasen samt deres individuelle "
"kapacitet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:27
msgid "Resources"
msgstr "Ressourcer"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:29
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`New` to create a new resource. On the blank record, enter "
"a :guilabel:`Name` for the new resource. In the :guilabel:`Capacity` field, "
"enter the maximum number of people the resource can accommodate. Then, "
"confirm the :guilabel:`Timezone` for this resource."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Ny` for at oprette en ny ressource. På den tomme post "
"skal du indtaste et :guilabel:`Navn` for den nye ressource. I "
"feltet :guilabel:`Kapacitet` skal du indtaste det maksimale antal personer, "
"som ressourcen kan rumme. Bekræft derefter :guilabel:`Tidszone` for denne "
"ressource."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:33
msgid ""
"If desired, select one or more :guilabel:`Linked Resource` from the drop-"
"down. This option designates one or more resources that can be used in "
"combination to handled a bigger demand."
msgstr ""
"Hvis ønsket skal du vælge en eller flere :guilabel:`Tilknyttet ressource` "
"fra rullemenuen. Denne mulighed angiver en eller flere ressourcer, der kan "
"bruges i kombination til at håndtere en større efterspørgsel."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:37
msgid ""
"*Linked resources* are only used when using the :ref:`auto-assign "
"<appointments/configure>` :guilabel:`Assignment Method`."
msgstr ""
"*Tilknyttede ressourcer* bruges kun, når der anvendes :ref:`auto-tildel "
"<appointments/configure>` :guilabel:`Tildelingsmetode`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:40
msgid ""
"Lastly, add a :guilabel:`Description` for this resource. The contents of "
"the :guilabel:`Description` tab are visible to customers when booking an "
"appointment online."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj til sidst en :guilabel:`Description` for denne ressource. Indholdet "
"af fanen :guilabel:`Description` er synligt for kunder, når de booker en "
"aftale online."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:44
msgid "Resource capacity"
msgstr "Ressourcekapacitet"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:46
msgid ""
"When booking an appointment based on resource availability, the website only "
"displays capacity up to `12`. This occurs even if the resource has a higher "
"capacity. To avoid this, a new *System Parameter* needs to be added to the "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Ved booking af en aftale baseret på resourcernes tilgængelighed viser "
"hjemmesiden kun kapacitet op til `12`. Dette sker, selvom ressourcen har en "
"højere kapacitet. For at undgå dette skal en ny *systemparameter* tilføjes "
"til databasen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:50
msgid ""
"First, ensure that :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` is enabled. Then, "
"navigate to the :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical --> Parameters --"
"> System Parameters`. Click :guilabel:`New` to add a new parameter."
msgstr ""
"Kontroller først, at :ref:`udviklertilstand <developer-mode>` er aktiveret. "
"Naviger derefter til :menuselection:`Indstillinger-appen --> Teknisk --> "
"Parametre --> Systemparametre`. Klik på :guilabel:`Ny` for at tilføje en ny "
"parameter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:54
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Key` field, enter "
"`appointment.resource_max_capacity_allowed`. In the :guilabel:`Value` field, "
"enter the maximum capacity that should be allowed. Click :icon:`fa-cloud-"
"upload` :guilabel:`(Save manually)` when finished."
msgstr ""
"Indtast `appointment.resource_max_capacity_allowed` i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Key`. Indtast den maksimale kapacitet, der skal tillades, "
"i feltet :guilabel:`Value`. Klik på :icon:`fa-cloud-upload` :guilabel:`(Gem "
"manuelt)`, når du er færdig."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:None
msgid "The new system parameter for capacity limits."
msgstr "Den nye systemparameter for kapacitetsgrænser."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:64
msgid "Appointment type configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguration af aftaletype"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:66
msgid ""
"Before appointments can be scheduled or booked, an appointment type must be "
"created. Navigate to the :menuselection:`Appointments` app dashboard and "
"click :guilabel:`New`. On the new blank record, enter "
"an :guilabel:`Appointment Title`, then set a :guilabel:`Duration` for this "
"appointment type."
msgstr ""
"Før aftaler kan planlægges eller bookes, skal en aftaletype oprettes. "
"Naviger til :menuselection:`Aftaler`-appens dashboard og klik "
"på :guilabel:`Ny`. På den nye tomme post skal du indtaste "
"en :guilabel:`Aftaletitel` og derefter angive en :guilabel:`Varighed` for "
"denne aftaletype."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:70
msgid ""
"Next, set a :guilabel:`Pre-Booking Time`. This is the minimum amount of time "
"between when an appointment can be booked and when the appointment can "
"begin. If the :guilabel:`Pre-Booking Time` is `1` hour, appointments must be "
"booked *at least* `1` hour in advance."
msgstr ""
"Angiv derefter en :guilabel:`Præ-bookningstid`. Dette er den mindste tid "
"mellem, hvornår en aftale kan bookes, og hvornår aftalen kan begynde. "
"Hvis :guilabel:`Præ-bookningstid` er `1` time, skal aftaler bookes *mindst* "
"`1` time i forvejen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:75
msgid ""
"An appointment type is created for `Tennis Courts`, with "
"a :guilabel:`Duration` of `1` hour, and a :guilabel:`Pre-Booking Time` of "
"`1` hour. At `02:00` PM, a customer attempts to book an appointment for the "
"same day at `02:45` pm. The first available time is `04:00` pm."
msgstr ""
"Der oprettes en aftaletype for `Tennisbaner` med en :guilabel:`Varighed` på "
"`1` time og en :guilabel:`Præ-bookningstid` på `1` time. Kl. `02:00`, "
"forsøger en kunde at booke en aftale samme dag kl. `02:45`. Det første "
"ledige tidspunkt er kl. `04:00`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:0
msgid "An example of the booking calendar showing available times."
msgstr "Et eksempel på bookingkalenderen, der viser tilgængelige tidspunkter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:82
msgid "Select a :guilabel:`Scheduling Window`:"
msgstr "Vælg et :guilabel:`Planlægningsvindue`:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:84
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Available now` to allow customers to book an appointment "
"immediately. Use the :guilabel:`Up to X days into the future` field to "
"define how far in advance customers can schedule appointments. For example, "
"if `14` is entered, customers cannot book anything more than 14 days from "
"the current date."
msgstr ""
"Vælg :guilabel:`Tilgængelig nu` for at tillade kunder at booke en aftale med "
"det samme. Brug feltet :guilabel:`Op til X dage frem i tiden` til at "
"definere, hvor langt frem kunder kan planlægge aftaler. Hvis der f.eks. "
"indtastes `14`, kan kunder ikke booke noget mere end 14 dage fra den "
"aktuelle dato."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:88
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Within a date range` to limit bookings to a specific range "
"of dates. After selecting this option, click the :guilabel:`From` "
"and :guilabel:`to` fields, and use the calendar pop-up window to customize "
"the date and time range."
msgstr ""
"Vælg :guilabel:`Inden for et datointerval` for at begrænse bookinger til et "
"specifikt datointerval. Efter at have valgt denne mulighed skal du klikke på "
"felterne :guilabel:`Fra` og :guilabel:`til` og bruge kalenderpopup-vinduet "
"til at tilpasse dato- og tidsintervallet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:92
msgid ""
"Update the :guilabel:`Allow Cancelling` field to limit the amount of time "
"before an appointment where a customer can cancel. If this setting is "
"enabled, customers are unable to cancel within the designated time frame."
msgstr ""
"Opdater feltet :guilabel:`Tillad annullering` for at begrænse, hvor lang tid "
"før en aftale en kunde kan annullere. Hvis denne indstilling er aktiveret, "
"kan kunder ikke annullere inden for den angivne tidsramme."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:97
msgid ""
"If a customer does try to cancel within the time frame, they receive an "
"error message with contact information. If the appointment is for a "
"resource, the contact details are for the user that created the appointment "
"type. If the appointment is for a user, the contact details are for the user "
"the appointment is with."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en kunde forsøger at annullere inden for tidsrammen, modtager de en "
"fejlmeddelelse med kontaktoplysninger. Hvis aftalen er for en ressource, er "
"kontaktoplysningerne for den bruger, der oprettede aftaletype. Hvis aftalen "
"er for en bruger, er kontaktoplysningerne for den bruger, aftalen er med."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:0
msgid "An example of the message a customer sees when cancelling."
msgstr "Et eksempel på den meddelelse, en kunde ser ved annullering."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:105
msgid ""
"Next, designate whether this appointment type is based on :guilabel:`Users` "
"or :guilabel:`Resources`, by selecting the appropriate radio button. If it "
"is based on users, select one or more :guilabel:`Users` in the drop-down. If "
"it is based on :ref:`resources <appointments/resources>`, select one or "
"more :guilabel:`Resources` in the drop-down."
msgstr ""
"Angiv derefter, om denne aftaletype er baseret på :guilabel:`Brugere` "
"eller :guilabel:`Ressourcer` ved at vælge den relevante radioknap. Hvis den "
"er baseret på brugere, skal du vælge en eller flere :guilabel:`Brugere` i "
"rullemenuen. Hvis den er baseret på :ref:`ressourcer <appointments/"
"resources>`, skal du vælge en eller flere :guilabel:`Ressourcer` i "
"rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:111
msgid ""
"User-based appointment types can be used for scheduling sales meetings and "
"demos, as well as recruiting interviews."
msgstr ""
"Brugerbaserede aftaletyper kan bruges til planlægning af salgsmøder og "
"demoer samt rekrutteringsinterviews."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:114
msgid ""
"Resource-based appointment types can be used for scheduling time in specific "
"rooms or locations."
msgstr ""
"Ressourcebaserede aftaletyper kan bruges til planlægning af tid i specifikke "
"rum eller lokationer."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:116
msgid ""
"Selecting :guilabel:`Resources` in the :guilabel:`Availability on` field "
"reveals the :guilabel:`Manage Capacities` option. If selected, the "
"appointment limits the number of participants based on the capacity of the "
"resources selected."
msgstr ""
"Valg af :guilabel:`Ressourcer` i feltet :guilabel:`Tilgængelighed på` "
"afslører indstillingen :guilabel:`Administrer kapaciteter`. Hvis den er "
"valgt, begrænser aftalen antallet af deltagere baseret på kapaciteten af de "
"valgte ressourcer."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:120
msgid ""
"Choose an :guilabel:`Assignment Method` by selecting the appropriate radio "
"button:"
msgstr ""
"Vælg en :guilabel:`Tildelingsmetode` ved at vælge den relevante radioknap:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:122
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pick User/Resource then Time`: customers select from a list of "
"available users/resources, then select an open time slot."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vælg bruger/ressource derefter tid`: kunder vælger fra en liste "
"over tilgængelige brugere/ressourcer og vælger derefter en ledig tidsplads."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:124
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Select Time then User/Resource`: customers choose a date and "
"time, then select from the list of available users/resources."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vælg tid derefter bruger/ressource`: kunder vælger en dato og tid "
"og vælger derefter fra listen over tilgængelige brugere/ressourcer."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:126
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Select Time then auto-assign`: customers select a time slot and "
"are automatically assigned a user/resource."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vælg tid derefter auto-tildel`: kunder vælger en tidsplads og får "
"automatisk tildelt en bruger/ressource."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:130
msgid "Schedule tab"
msgstr "Fanen Tidsplan"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:132
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Schedule` tab is used to outline when this appointment type "
"is to be made available. The settings define the time slots shown on the "
"booking page."
msgstr ""
"Fanen :guilabel:`Tidsplan` bruges til at angive, hvornår denne aftaletype "
"skal gøres tilgængelig. Indstillingerne definerer de tidspladser, der vises "
"på bookingsiden."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:135
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` to create a new time frame. Select a day of the "
"week from the :guilabel:`Every` drop-down menu, then update the times in "
"the :guilabel:`From` and :guilabel:`To` fields. Click the :icon:`fa-trash-"
"o` :guilabel:`(trash)` icon to delete an entry. Multiple entries can be "
"included for a single day."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Tilføj en linje` for at oprette en ny tidsramme. Vælg en "
"ugedag fra rullemenuen :guilabel:`Hver`, og opdater derefter tiderne i "
"felterne :guilabel:`Fra` og :guilabel:`Til`. Klik på ikonet :icon:`fa-trash-"
"o` :guilabel:`(papirkurv)` for at slette en post. Flere poster kan "
"inkluderes for en enkelt dag."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:141
msgid ""
"If an appointment should not be available at specific times, such as when "
"users are taking lunch, include time slots before and after."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en aftale ikke skal være tilgængelig på bestemte tidspunkter, såsom når "
"brugere holder frokost, skal du inkludere tidspladser før og efter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:0
msgid "An example of the Schedule tab in an appointment."
msgstr "Et eksempel på fanen Tidsplan i en aftale."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:148
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:234
msgid "Options tab"
msgstr "Záložka možnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:150
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Options` tab is used to customize the display options for "
"this appointment, as well as notification settings for customers and users."
msgstr ""
"Fanen :guilabel:`Indstillinger` bruges til at tilpasse visningsindstillinger "
"for denne aftale samt meddelelsesindstillinger for kunder og brugere."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:153
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Front-End Display` field determines how the appointment is "
"presented on the website to customers. Select the :guilabel:`Show Pictures` "
"radio button to publish the default pictures of the user or resources for "
"this appointment on the website."
msgstr ""
"Feltet :guilabel:`Front-end-visning` bestemmer, hvordan aftalen præsenteres "
"på hjemmesiden for kunder. Vælg radioknappen :guilabel:`Vis billeder` for at "
"offentliggøre standardbillederne af brugeren eller ressourcerne for denne "
"aftale på hjemmesiden."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:157
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Timezone` and :guilabel:`Location` fields automatically "
"populate for resource appointments, based on where the resource is located. "
"For user-based appointments, the :guilabel:`Location` field defaults to an "
"`Online Meeting`, with a :guilabel:`Videoconference Link` automatically "
"generated. If this should not be an online meeting, select a different "
"option in the :guilabel:`Location` field."
msgstr ""
"Felterne :guilabel:`Tidszone` og :guilabel:`Lokation` udfyldes automatisk "
"for ressourceaftaler baseret på, hvor ressourcen er placeret. For "
"brugerbaserede aftaler er standardværdien i feltet :guilabel:`Lokation` et "
"`onlinemøde` med et :guilabel:`Videokonferencelink`, der genereres "
"automatisk. Hvis dette ikke skal være et onlinemøde, skal du vælge en anden "
"mulighed i feltet :guilabel:`Lokation`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:163
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`Manual Confirmation` checkbox to require approval before "
"a meeting is accepted. If this feature is enabled, the appointment time slot "
"is still considered *reserved* until it is confirmed or rejected. Leave this "
"checkbox blank to automatically accept meetings created from this "
"appointment."
msgstr ""
"Marker afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Manuel bekræftelse` for at kræve "
"godkendelse, før et møde accepteres. Hvis denne funktion er aktiveret, "
"betragtes mødetidspunktet stadig som *reserveret*, indtil det bekræftes "
"eller afvises. Lad dette afkrydsningsfelt stå tomt for automatisk at "
"acceptere møder oprettet fra denne aftale."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:168
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Create Opportunities <appointments/create-opps>` feature adds an "
"opportunity to the **CRM** app for each scheduled appointment, which is "
"assigned to the responsible user. Tick the :guilabel:`Create Opportunities` "
"checkbox to enable this option."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen :doc:`Opret muligheder <appointments/create-opps>` tilføjer en "
"mulighed til **CRM**-appen for hver planlagt aftale, som tildeles den "
"ansvarlige bruger. Marker afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Opret muligheder` "
"for at aktivere denne indstilling."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:173
msgid ""
"This field is only visible if the **CRM** app is installed on the database."
msgstr ""
"Dette felt er kun synligt, hvis **CRM**-appen er installeret på databasen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:175
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Reminders` field is used to set how customers are to be "
"contacted before the appointment time. Select one or more options from the "
"drop-down, based on the communication method, and the time frame."
msgstr ""
"Feltet :guilabel:`Påmindelser` bruges til at angive, hvordan kunder skal "
"kontaktes før aftaletidspunktet. Vælg en eller flere muligheder fra "
"rullemenuen baseret på kommunikationsmetode og tidsramme."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:179
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`Allow Guests` checkbox to grant customers the ability to "
"add additional guests when registering for an appointment."
msgstr ""
"Marker afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Tillad gæster` for at give kunder "
"mulighed for at tilføje yderligere gæster, når de registrerer sig til en "
"aftale."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:185
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:204
msgid "Questions tab"
msgstr "Spørgsmålsfane"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:187
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Questions` tab can be used to prompt customers for additional "
"information while they are booking an appointment. Click :guilabel:`Add a "
"line` to add a new question."
msgstr ""
"Fanen :guilabel:`Spørgsmål` kan bruges til at bede kunder om yderligere "
"oplysninger, mens de booker en aftale. Klik på :guilabel:`Tilføj en linje` "
"for at tilføje et nyt spørgsmål."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:190
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Create Questions` pop-up window, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Question`, then choose an :guilabel:`Answer Type`."
msgstr ""
"I pop op-vinduet :guilabel:`Opret spørgsmål` "
"indtastes :guilabel:`Spørgsmål`, og derefter vælges en :guilabel:`Svartype`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:193
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`Mandatory Answer` checkbox to require customers to "
"answer this question before they are allowed to book an appointment. "
"Click :guilabel:`Save & New` to add another question, or :guilabel:`Save & "
"Close` when finished."
msgstr ""
"Marker afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Obligatorisk svar` for at kræve, at "
"kunder besvarer dette spørgsmål, før de får lov til at booke en aftale. Klik "
"på :guilabel:`Gem og ny` for at tilføje endnu et spørgsmål "
"eller :guilabel:`Gem og luk`, når du er færdig."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:198
msgid "Messages tab"
msgstr "Fanen beskeder"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:200
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Messages` tab is used by the business to provide additional "
"information to customers regarding this appointment type."
msgstr ""
"Fanen :guilabel:`Beskeder` bruges af virksomheden til at give yderligere "
"oplysninger til kunder vedrørende denne aftaletype."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:204
msgid ""
"The content in the :guilabel:`Messages` tab is visible to customers and "
"website visitors."
msgstr ""
"Indholdet i fanen :guilabel:`Beskeder` er synligt for kunder og besøgende på "
"hjemmesiden."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:206
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Introduction Message` field, add a short description of "
"the appointment type. This can include the topic of the appointment, a "
"meeting agenda, or an introduction to the users responsible for the meeting."
msgstr ""
"I feltet :guilabel:`Introduktionsbesked` tilføjes en kort beskrivelse af "
"aftaletypen. Dette kan inkludere emnet for aftalen, en mødedagsorden eller "
"en introduktion til de brugere, der er ansvarlige for mødet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:210
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Extra Message on Confirmation` is displayed to a customer "
"after they have booked a meeting. Add any additional information here that "
"the customer should be aware of. This can include parking information, last "
"minute rules, or additional instructions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ekstra besked ved bekræftelse` vises til en kunde, efter de har "
"booket et møde. Tilføj eventuelle yderligere oplysninger her, som kunden bør "
"være opmærksom på. Dette kan inkludere parkeringsoplysninger, regler på "
"sidste øjeblik eller yderligere instruktioner."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:215
msgid "Publishing an appointment"
msgstr "Publicere en aftale"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:217
msgid ""
"When an appointment is ready to publish, click the :guilabel:`Go to Website` "
"smart button at the top of the record. Then, slide the :icon:`fa-toggle-"
"off` :guilabel:`Unpublished` icon to :icon:`fa-toggle-"
"on` :guilabel:`Published`."
msgstr ""
"Når en aftale er klar til at blive publiceret, klikkes på smart-"
"knappen :guilabel:`Gå til hjemmeside` øverst på posten. Skub "
"derefter :icon:`fa-toggle-off` :guilabel:`Upubliceret`-ikonet til :icon:`fa-"
"toggle-on` :guilabel:`Publiceret`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:3
msgid "Create opportunities from appointments"
msgstr "Opret muligheder fra aftaler"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:5
msgid ""
"When creating a new appointment type in the **Appointments** application, "
"users have the option to create new *opportunities* with information from "
"new bookings. This option captures information from scheduled appointments "
"and creates opportunities in the **CRM** app."
msgstr ""
"Ved oprettelse af en ny aftaletype i **Aftaler**-applikationen har brugere "
"mulighed for at oprette nye *muligheder* med oplysninger fra nye bookinger. "
"Denne indstilling indfanger oplysninger fra planlagte aftaler og opretter "
"muligheder i **CRM**-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:10
msgid ""
"This option is only available if the **CRM** application is installed on the "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Denne indstilling er kun tilgængelig, hvis **CRM**-applikationen er "
"installeret på databasen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:15
msgid ""
"Navigate to the **Appointments** app dashboard. Click :guilabel:`New` "
"to :doc:`create a new appointment type <../appointments>`. To edit an "
"existing appointment type, click :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Action` at the "
"far-right of the appointment line, to open the drop-down menu, then "
"click :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`Edit`."
msgstr ""
"Gå til dashboardet i **Aftaler**-appen. Klik på :guilabel:`Ny` for "
"at :doc:`oprette en ny aftaletype <../appointments>`. For at redigere en "
"eksisterende aftaletype klikkes på :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Handling` helt "
"til højre på aftalelinjen for at åbne rullemenuen, og klik derefter "
"på :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`Rediger`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:None
msgid "The edit button on an appointment type record."
msgstr "Redigeringsknappen på en aftaletypepost."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:23
msgid ""
"On the appointment type record, click the :guilabel:`Options` tab, and tick "
"the :guilabel:`Create Opportunities` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"På aftaletypeposten klik på fanen :guilabel:`Indstillinger`, og marker "
"afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Opret muligheder`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:None
msgid "The options tab on an appointment type form."
msgstr "Fanen Indstillinger på en aftaletypeformular."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:30
msgid "Add questions"
msgstr "Tilføj spørgsmål"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:32
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Questions` tab allows users to :ref:`add questions "
"<appointments/questions>` to the appointment booking page. When customers "
"are booking an appointment slot, they are prompted to answer these "
"questions. The information provided by customers is available in "
"the :ref:`new opportunity <appointments/new-opp>`. Adding questions to the "
"appointment type is optional. However, the additional information captured "
"by the questions can be useful later in the sales pipeline."
msgstr ""
"Fanen :guilabel:`Spørgsmål` giver brugere mulighed for at :ref:`tilføje "
"spørgsmål <appointments/questions>` til aftalebookingsiden. Når kunder "
"booker en aftaletid, bliver de bedt om at besvare disse spørgsmål. De "
"oplysninger, som kunder giver, er tilgængelige i den :ref:`nye mulighed "
"<appointments/new-opp>`. Det er valgfrit at tilføje spørgsmål til "
"aftaletypen. De yderligere oplysninger, der indfanges via spørgsmålene, kan "
"dog være nyttige senere i salgspipelinen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:39
msgid ""
"A furniture company creates a new appointment type for sales demos. "
"Customers reserve time with salespeople to discuss their furniture and "
"design needs. However, because the time is limited to only thirty minute "
"increments, salespeople do not have the time to show all of the available "
"furniture styles in every call. They add questions to the appointment type "
"to prompt customers to provide additional information about the products and "
"services they are interested in. Not only does this help when preparing for "
"the demo, it also provides clarity further along in the sales process."
msgstr ""
"En møbelvirksomhed opretter en ny aftaletype til salgsdemoer. Kunder "
"reserverer tid med sælgere for at diskutere deres møbel- og designbehov. Men "
"fordi tiden er begrænset til kun tredive minutters intervaller, har sælgerne "
"ikke tid til at vise alle tilgængelige møbelstilarter i hvert opkald. De "
"tilføjer spørgsmål til aftaletypen for at bede kunder om at give yderligere "
"oplysninger om de produkter og tjenester, de er interesserede i. Det hjælper "
"ikke kun ved forberedelse til demoen, det giver også klarhed længere fremme "
"i salgsprocessen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:0
msgid "An appointment booking form with custom questions."
msgstr "En aftalebookingformular med tilpassede spørgsmål."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:53
msgid "Viewing the new opportunity"
msgstr "Visning af den nye mulighed"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:55
msgid ""
"To view opportunities created from appointments, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`CRM` app dashboard. If necessary, remove any filters "
"from the search bar. Then, click the Kanban card for the appropriate "
"opportunity to open it."
msgstr ""
"For at se muligheder oprettet fra aftaler skal du navigere til dashboardet "
"i :menuselection:`CRM`-appen. Fjern om nødvendigt eventuelle filtre fra "
"søgelinjen. Klik derefter på Kanban-kortet for den relevante mulighed for at "
"åbne den."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:59
msgid ""
"The contact information from the appointment is added to the opportunity "
"record. The answers the customer provided to the optional questions are "
"included in the :guilabel:`Internal Notes` tab. The scheduled appointment is "
"listed in the *Chatter* of the record, and can be edited from there."
msgstr ""
"Kontaktoplysningerne fra aftalen tilføjes til mulighedsposten. De svar, som "
"kunden gav på de valgfrie spørgsmål, er inkluderet i "
"fanen :guilabel:`Interne noter`. Den planlagte aftale er angivet i *Chatten* "
"på posten og kan redigeres derfra."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:None
msgid ""
"The chatter of an opportunity in the CRM with the scheduled appointment "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Chatten for en mulighed i CRM'en med oplysninger om den planlagte aftale."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:67
msgid ""
"If an opportunity is created from a :ref:`resource based <appointments/"
"resources>` appointment type, the user who created the appointment type is "
"listed as the :guilabel:`Salesperson` for the opportunity. If it is created "
"from a user based appointment, the user the appointment is scheduled with is "
"assigned as the :guilabel:`Salesperson`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en mulighed oprettes fra en :ref:`ressourcebaseret <appointments/"
"resources>` aftaletype, vises den bruger, der oprettede aftaletypen, "
"som :guilabel:`Sælger` for muligheden. Hvis den oprettes fra en "
"brugerbaseret aftale, tildeles den bruger, som aftalen er planlagt med, "
"som :guilabel:`Sælger`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:3
msgid "Google reserve integration"
msgstr "Google Reserve-integration"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:5
msgid ""
"Google Reserve lets customers book appointments directly from Google Search, "
"Google Maps, and the Google Assistant. By connecting Odoo **Appointments** "
"to Google Reserve, bookings are added directly into Odoo without customers "
"needing to visit the company website."
msgstr ""
"Google Reserve lader kunder booke aftaler direkte fra Google-søgning, Google "
"Maps og Google Assistent. Ved at forbinde Odoo **Aftaler** til Google "
"Reserve tilføjes bookinger direkte i Odoo uden at kunder behøver at besøge "
"virksomhedens hjemmeside."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:14
msgid ""
"First, navigate to the :guilabel:`Apps` application. Then, remove "
"the :guilabel:`Apps` filter from the search bar and type in `Google`. "
"Click :guilabel:`Install` on the :guilabel:`Appointment Google Reserve` "
"module."
msgstr ""
"Naviger først til applikationen :guilabel:`Apps`. Fjern derefter "
"filteret :guilabel:`Apps` fra søgelinjen og indtast `Google`. Klik "
"på :guilabel:`Installer` på modulet :guilabel:`Appointment Google Reserve`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:None
msgid "The Google Reserve module in the Odoo apps application."
msgstr "Google Reserve-modulet i Odoo apps-applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:21
msgid ""
"Next, navigate to the :menuselection:`Appointments` application. Open an "
"existing appointment type, or click :guilabel:`New` to :ref:`create a new "
"one <appointments/configure>`. Then click the :guilabel:`Google Bookings` "
"tab."
msgstr ""
"Naviger derefter til :menuselection:`Aftaler`-applikationen. Åbn en "
"eksisterende aftaletype, eller klik på :guilabel:`Ny` for at :ref:`oprette "
"en ny <appointments/configure>`. Klik derefter på fanen :guilabel:`Google "
"Bookings`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:25
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Google Reserve Merchant` field, and select an option "
"from the drop-down, or click :guilabel:`Create` to open "
"the :guilabel:`Create Google Reserve Merchant` form."
msgstr ""
"Klik på feltet :guilabel:`Google Reserve Merchant`, og vælg en mulighed fra "
"rullemenuen, eller klik på :guilabel:`Opret` for at åbne "
"formularen :guilabel:`Opret Google Reserve Merchant`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:28
msgid ""
"On the form, enter all required information. The business address **must** "
"match exactly what appears on Google Maps. Click :guilabel:`Save & Close`."
msgstr ""
"Indtast alle nødvendige oplysninger på formularen. Forretningsadressen "
"**skal** matche nøjagtigt, hvad der vises på Google Maps. Klik "
"på :guilabel:`Gem & luk`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:None
msgid "A create new google merchant form in the Appointments app."
msgstr "En formular til at oprette en ny Google-forhandler i Aftaler-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:34
msgid ""
"Once the new merchant has been created, click :guilabel:`Synchronize with "
"Google Reserve`. The initial synchronization can take up to 24 hours to "
"propagate to Google's systems."
msgstr ""
"Når den nye forhandler er oprettet, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Synkroniser "
"med Google Reserve`. Den indledende synkronisering kan tage op til 24 timer "
"at sprede til Googles systemer."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:38
msgid ""
"Ensure that the business address matches the Google Maps listing precisely, "
"including formatting and unit numbers. Mismatches may cause synchronization "
"to fail or prevent the listing from appearing on Google."
msgstr ""
"Sørg for, at forretningsadressen matcher Google Maps-registreringen præcist, "
"inklusive formatering og enhedsnumre. Uoverensstemmelser kan forårsage, at "
"synkroniseringen fejler eller forhindre registreringen i at vises på Google."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:5
msgid "Calendar"
msgstr "Kalender"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo **Calendar** is a scheduling app that allows users to integrate a "
"company's business flow into a single management platform. By integrating "
"with the other apps in Odoo's ecosystem, **Calendar** allows users to "
"schedule and organize meetings, schedule events, plan employee appraisals, "
"coordinate projects, and more."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **Kalender** er en planlægningsapp, der giver brugere mulighed for at "
"integrere en virksomheds forretningsflow i en enkelt "
"administrationsplatform. Ved at integrere med de andre apps i Odoos "
"økosystem giver **Kalender** brugere mulighed for at planlægge og organisere "
"møder, planlægge arrangementer, planlægge medarbejderevalueringer, "
"koordinere projekter og mere."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:12
msgid ""
"Upon opening the :menuselection:`Calendar app`, users have an overview of "
"their current meetings. The selected view option appears as "
"a :guilabel:`Day`, :guilabel:`Week`, :guilabel:`Month`, or :guilabel:`Year` "
"drop-down menu. Under the view options drop-down menu, users can also enable "
"or disable :guilabel:`Show weekends`."
msgstr ""
"Ved åbning af :menuselection:`Kalender-appen` har brugere en oversigt over "
"deres aktuelle møder. Den valgte visningsmulighed vises som "
"en :guilabel:`Dag`-, :guilabel:`Uge`-, :guilabel:`Måned`- "
"eller :guilabel:`År`-rullemenuen. Under rullemenuen for visningsmuligheder "
"kan brugere også aktivere eller deaktivere :guilabel:`Vis weekender`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:None
msgid "Overview of Calendar app."
msgstr "Oversigt over Kalender-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:21
msgid ""
"Depending on the selected view option, users can click the :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"left` :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(left or right arrow)` buttons to "
"switch between days, weeks, etc., and switch back to the current day with "
"the :guilabel:`Today` button."
msgstr ""
"Afhængigt af den valgte visningsmulighed kan brugere klikke på :icon:`oi-"
"arrow-left` :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(venstre eller højre pil)` "
"knapperne for at skifte mellem dage, uger osv. og skifte tilbage til den "
"aktuelle dag med knappen :guilabel:`I dag`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:26
msgid "Sync third-party calendars"
msgstr "Synkroniser tredjepartskalendere"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:28
msgid ""
"Users can sync Odoo with existing :doc:`Outlook <calendar/outlook>` and/"
"or :doc:`Google <calendar/google>` calendars, by heading "
"to :menuselection:`Calendar app --> Configuration --> Settings`. From here, "
"enter :guilabel:`Client ID` and :guilabel:`Client Secret`. There is also an "
"option to pause synchronization by ticking the checkbox, or automating "
"synchronization by keeping it blank."
msgstr ""
"Brugere kan synkronisere Odoo med eksisterende :doc:`Outlook <calendar/"
"outlook>`- og/eller :doc:`Google <calendar/google>`-kalendere ved at gå "
"til :menuselection:`Kalender-app --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`. "
"Indtast herfra :guilabel:`Klient-id` og :guilabel:`Klienthemmelighed`. Der "
"er også en mulighed for at sætte synkronisering på pause ved at markere "
"afkrydsningsfeltet eller automatisere synkronisering ved at holde det tomt."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:34
msgid ""
"Once the desired configurations are complete, click :guilabel:`Save` before "
"moving on."
msgstr ""
"Når de ønskede konfigurationer er fuldført, klik på :guilabel:`Save`, før du "
"fortsætter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:36
msgid ""
"Events created in synced calendars automatically appear across the "
"integrated platforms."
msgstr ""
"Arrangementer oprettet i synkroniserede kalendere vises automatisk på tværs "
"af de integrerede platforme."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:39
msgid ":doc:`Synchronize Outlook calendar with Odoo <calendar/outlook>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Synkroniser Outlook-kalender med Odoo <calendar/outlook>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:40
msgid ":doc:`Synchronize Google calendar with Odoo <calendar/google>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Synkroniser Google-kalender med Odoo <calendar/google>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:43
msgid "Create activities from chatter"
msgstr "Opret aktiviteter fra chatter"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:45
msgid ""
"Instantly create new meetings anywhere in Odoo through an individual "
"record's chatter, like in a **CRM** opportunity card or task in the "
"**Project** app."
msgstr ""
"Opret øjeblikkeligt nye møder hvor som helst i Odoo gennem en individuel "
"records chatter, som i et **CRM** opportunity-kort eller en opgave i "
"**Projekt** appen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:48
msgid ""
"From the chatter, click on the :guilabel:`Activity` button. In "
"the :guilabel:`Schedule Activity` pop-up window, select the "
"desired :guilabel:`Activity Type`, which populates a set of buttons, "
"depending on the activity."
msgstr ""
"Fra chatteren skal du klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Activity`. I pop-up-"
"vinduet :guilabel:`Schedule Activity` skal du vælge den "
"ønskede :guilabel:`Activity Type`, som viser et sæt knapper, afhængigt af "
"aktiviteten."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:52
msgid ""
"Activities that involve other schedules, like :guilabel:`Meeting` "
"or :guilabel:`Call for Demo`, link to the **Calendar** app. Select one of "
"these activities to link to the **Calendar** app, then "
"hit :guilabel:`Schedule` to navigate back to the app."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviteter der involverer andre tidsplaner, som :guilabel:`Meeting` "
"eller :guilabel:`Call for Demo`, linker til **Kalender** appen. Vælg en af "
"disse aktiviteter for at linke til **Kalender** appen, og tryk derefter "
"på :guilabel:`Schedule` for at navigere tilbage til appen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:57
msgid ":doc:`Schedule activities in Odoo <../essentials/activities>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Planlæg aktiviteter i Odoo <../essentials/activities>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:60
msgid "Plan an event"
msgstr "Planlæg et arrangement"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:62
msgid ""
"To put an event on the calendar, open the :menuselection:`Calendar app`, and "
"click into the target date. On the :guilabel:`New Event` pop-up window that "
"appears, start by adding the event title."
msgstr ""
"For at lægge et arrangement i kalenderen skal du "
"åbne :menuselection:`Kalender-appen` og klikke på måldatoen. I pop op-"
"vinduet :guilabel:`Nyt arrangement`, der vises, skal du starte med at "
"tilføje arrangementets titel."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:None
msgid "Schedule an event window on Calendar app."
msgstr "Planlæg et arrangement-vindue i Kalender-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:68
msgid ""
"The target date auto-populates in the :guilabel:`Start` field. This can be "
"changed by clicking into the date section, and selecting a date from the "
"calendar. For multi-day events, select the end date in the second field, "
"then click :guilabel:`Apply`."
msgstr ""
"Måldatoen udfyldes automatisk i feltet :guilabel:`Start`. Dette kan ændres "
"ved at klikke i datofeltet og vælge en dato fra kalenderen. For "
"flerdagesarrangementer skal du vælge slutdatoen i det andet felt og derefter "
"klikke på :guilabel:`Anvend`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:72
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`All Day` checkbox if there is no specific start or end "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Marker afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Hele dagen`, hvis der ikke er et "
"specifikt start- eller sluttidspunkt."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:74
msgid ""
"For events with specific start and stop times, ensure the :guilabel:`All "
"Day` checkbox is unticked to enable time selection. With the :guilabel:`All "
"Day` checkbox unticked, time selections appear in the :guilabel:`Start` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"For arrangementer med specifikke start- og sluttidspunkter skal du sikre "
"dig, at afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Hele dagen` ikke er markeret for at "
"aktivere tidsvalg. Når afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Hele dagen` ikke er "
"markeret, vises tidsvalg i feltet :guilabel:`Start`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:78
msgid ""
"The signed-in user auto-populates as the first attendee. "
"Additional :guilabel:`Attendees` can be added or created from here, as well."
msgstr ""
"Den bruger, der er logget ind, udfyldes automatisk som den første deltager. "
"Yderligere :guilabel:`Deltagere` kan også tilføjes eller oprettes herfra."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:81
msgid ""
"For virtual meetings, copy and paste the URL into the space provided in "
"the :guilabel:`Videocall URL` field. Or, click :icon:`fa-"
"plus` :guilabel:`Video` to create a link."
msgstr ""
"For virtuelle møder skal du kopiere og indsætte URL'en i det angivne felt i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Videocall URL`. Eller klik på :icon:`fa-"
"plus` :guilabel:`Video` for at oprette et link."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:84
msgid ""
"Next, either create the event by clicking :guilabel:`Save & Close`, or "
"select :guilabel:`More Options` to further configure the event."
msgstr ""
"Opret derefter arrangementet ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Gem og luk`, eller "
"vælg :guilabel:`Flere muligheder` for at konfigurere arrangementet "
"yderligere."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:88
msgid ""
"Once the event is created, users can click into the virtual meeting directly "
"from the calendar event to access more configuration options."
msgstr ""
"Når arrangementet er oprettet, kan brugere klikke direkte ind i det "
"virtuelle møde fra kalenderarrangementet for at få adgang til flere "
"konfigurationsmuligheder."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:None
msgid "The full event form for a new calendar event."
msgstr "Den komplette arrangementformular for et nyt kalenderarrangement."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:94
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Description` field allows users to add additional information "
"and details about the meeting."
msgstr ""
"Feltet :guilabel:`Beskrivelse` giver brugerne mulighed for at tilføje "
"yderligere oplysninger og detaljer om mødet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:97
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`More Options` to navigate to the meeting form, which "
"provides additional configurations for the event:"
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Flere muligheder` for at navigere til mødeformularen, som "
"giver yderligere konfigurationer for arrangementet:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:100
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Duration`: Define the length of the meeting in :guilabel:`hours`, "
"or toggle the :guilabel:`All Day` switch."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Varighed`: Definer mødets længde i :guilabel:`timer`, eller "
"slå :guilabel:`Hele dagen`-kontakten til."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:102
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Organizer`: This is defaulted to the current Odoo user. Select a "
"new one from existing users, or create and edit a new user."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Arrangør`: Dette er som standard den aktuelle Odoo-bruger. Vælg "
"en ny blandt eksisterende brugere, eller opret og rediger en ny bruger."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:104
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tags`: Add tags to the event, like `Customer Meeting` or "
"`Internal Meeting`. These can be searched and filtered in the **Calendar** "
"app when organizing multiple events."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tags`: Tilføj tags til arrangementet, som `Kundemøde` eller "
"`Internt møde`. Disse kan søges og filtreres i **Kalender**-appen, når man "
"organiserer flere arrangementer."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:106
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Calendar description`: Add additional information or details "
"about the meeting."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Calendar description`: tilføj yderligere information eller "
"detaljer om mødet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:107
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reminders`: Select notification options to send to attendees. "
"Choose a default notification, or configure new reminders."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Påmindelser`: Vælg meddelelsesmuligheder, der skal sendes til "
"deltagere. Vælg en standardmeddelelse, eller konfigurer nye påmindelser."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:109
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Recurrent`: Tick the checkbox to create a recurring meeting. Once "
"selected, this opens new fields:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Gentaget`: Marker afkrydsningsfeltet for at oprette et "
"tilbagevendende møde. Når det er valgt, åbnes nye felter:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:112
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Repeat`: Select the recurring period of this meeting. Depending "
"on what type of recurrence has been selected, a subsequent field appears, in "
"which users can indicate when the meeting should recur. For example, "
"if :guilabel:`Monthly` is selected as the :guilabel:`Repeat` option, a new "
"field appears, in which the user decides on what :guilabel:`Day of Month` "
"the meeting should recur."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Gentag`: Vælg den tilbagevendende periode for dette møde. "
"Afhængigt af hvilken type gentagelse der er valgt, vises et efterfølgende "
"felt, hvor brugere kan angive, hvornår mødet skal gentages. Hvis "
"f.eks. :guilabel:`Månedligt` er valgt som :guilabel:`Gentag`-mulighed, vises "
"et nyt felt, hvor brugeren beslutter, på hvilken :guilabel:`Dag i måneden` "
"mødet skal gentages."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:117
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Until`: Select the limited :guilabel:`Number of repetitions` this "
"meeting should recur, the :guilabel:`End date` of when the recurrences "
"should stop, or if the meetings should recur :guilabel:`Forever`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Indtil`: Vælg det begrænsede :guilabel:`Antal gentagelser`, som "
"dette møde skal gentages, :guilabel:`Slutdatoen` for, hvornår gentagelserne "
"skal stoppe, eller om møderne skal gentages :guilabel:`For evigt`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:120
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Timezone`: Select the timezone for which this meeting time is "
"specified."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tidszone`: Vælg den tidszone, som dette mødetidspunkt er angivet "
"for."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:123
msgid "Coordinate with teams' availability"
msgstr "Koordiner med teams' tilgængelighed"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:125
msgid ""
"When scheduling an event for multiple users, on the **Calendar** app "
"dashboard, tick the checkbox next to :guilabel:`Attendees` to view team "
"members' availability. Tick (or untick) the checkbox next to listed users to "
"show (or hide) individual calendars."
msgstr ""
"Når du planlægger en begivenhed for flere brugere, skal du på **Kalender**-"
"appens dashboard markere afkrydsningsfeltet ved siden "
"af :guilabel:`Deltagere` for at se teammedlemmers tilgængelighed. Marker "
"(eller afmarker) afkrydsningsfeltet ved siden af listede brugere for at vise "
"(eller skjule) individuelle kalendere."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:None
msgid "View of Attendees section on Calendar app."
msgstr "Visning af afsnittet Deltagere i Kalender-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:135
msgid "Share Availabilities"
msgstr "Del ledige tider"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:137
msgid ""
"On the **Calendar** app main dashboard, click the :guilabel:`Share` button "
"at the top of the page, then select :guilabel:`Specific Slots` from the drop-"
"down. Next, click and drag to select the available times and dates on the "
"calendar to add them as options in the invitation."
msgstr ""
"På hovedsiden i **Kalender** appen skal du klikke på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Share` øverst på siden og derefter "
"vælge :guilabel:`Specific Slots` fra drop-down-menuen. Klik og træk derefter "
"for at vælge de tilgængelige tidspunkter og datoer i kalenderen for at "
"tilføje dem som valgmuligheder i invitationen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:None
msgid "Selecting availabilites on the Calendar dashboard."
msgstr "Valg af tilgængelighed på dashboard for Kalender."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:145
msgid ""
"To remove a selected time range, hover over the availability to click "
"the :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(trash)` icon."
msgstr ""
"For at fjerne et valgt tidsinterval skal du holde musen over "
"tilgængeligheden for at klikke på :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(papirkurv)`-"
"ikonet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:148
msgid ""
"Once availability has been selected, click :icon:`fa-"
"clipboard` :guilabel:`Copy Link` to copy a sharable link to the clipboard. "
"Or, click :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Configure` icon button to navigate to "
"the associated appointment."
msgstr ""
"Når tilgængelighed er valgt, klik på :icon:`fa-clipboard` :guilabel:`Kopiér "
"link` for at kopiere et delbart link til udklipsholderen. Eller klik "
"på :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Konfigurer` ikonknappen for at navigere til den "
"tilknyttede aftale."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:None
msgid "Share availability window on Calendar app."
msgstr "Vindue til deling af tilgængelighed i Kalender-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:155
msgid ""
"On the **Share Availabilities** form, enter an :guilabel:`Appointment "
"Title`. Confirm the correct user is selected in the :guilabel:`Users` field. "
"To add a meeting room to the appointment, click the :guilabel:`Location` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"I formularen **Del tilgængelighed** skal du angive "
"en :guilabel:`Aftaletitel`. Bekræft, at den korrekte bruger er valgt i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Brugere`. For at tilføje et mødelokale til aftalen skal du "
"klikke på feltet :guilabel:`Placering`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:160
msgid ""
"If nothing is selected in the :guilabel:`Location` field, the appointment "
"defaults to an *Online Meeting*."
msgstr ""
"Hvis intet er valgt i feltet :guilabel:`Placering`, er aftalen som standard "
"et *Onlinemøde*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:163
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Video Link` field, select the type of video call link that "
"will be used for the generated appointments. If this field is left blank, no "
"meeting URLs will be created."
msgstr ""
"I feltet :guilabel:`Videolink` skal du vælge den type videoopkaldslink, der "
"skal bruges til de genererede aftaler. Hvis dette felt efterlades tomt, "
"oprettes ingen møde-URL'er."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:166
msgid ""
"To allow attendees to invite others to the event, tick the :guilabel:`Allow "
"invitations` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"For at tillade deltagere at invitere andre til begivenheden skal du markere "
"afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Tillad invitationer`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:168
msgid ""
"Add a message in the :guilabel:`Introduction Message` field. This is used as "
"a description for the event. Add a message to the :guilabel:`Extra Message "
"on Confirmation` field to be displayed after the appointment is booked."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj en besked i feltet :guilabel:`Introduktionsbesked`. Denne bruges som "
"beskrivelse af begivenheden. Tilføj en besked til feltet :guilabel:`Ekstra "
"besked ved bekræftelse`, der skal vises, efter at aftalen er booket."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:172
msgid ""
"Click :icon:`fa-clipboard` :guilabel:`Save & Copy Link`. To futher customize "
"the appointment, click the :icon:`fa-expand` :guilabel:`(expand)` icon at "
"the top of the pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :icon:`fa-clipboard` :guilabel:`Gem og kopiér link`. For yderligere "
"at tilpasse aftalen skal du klikke på :icon:`fa-expand` :guilabel:`(udvid)` "
"ikonet øverst i pop op-vinduet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:175
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Preview` button to see how the appointment link looks "
"for attendees."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Forhåndsvisning`-knappen for at se, hvordan aftalelinket "
"ser ud for deltagere."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:177
msgid "Optionally, configure the following tabs:"
msgstr "Konfigurer eventuelt følgende faneblade:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:179
msgid ":ref:`calendar/appointment-schedule`"
msgstr ":ref:`calendar/appointment-schedule`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:180
msgid ":ref:`calendar/appointment-questions`"
msgstr ":ref:`calendar/appointment-questions`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:181
msgid ":ref:`calendar/appointment-messages`"
msgstr ":ref:`calendar/appointment-messages`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:182
msgid ":ref:`calendar/appointment-options`"
msgstr ":ref:`calendar/appointment-options`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:184
msgid ""
"Once the configurations are finished, click the :guilabel:`Share` button to "
"generate a link to send directly, or click :guilabel:`Publish` to publish "
"the appointment selection on the connected Odoo website."
msgstr ""
"Når konfigurationerne er færdige, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Del`-knappen "
"for at generere et link, der kan sendes direkte, eller klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Publicer` for at publicere aftalevalget på den tilsluttede "
"Odoo-hjemmeside."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:191
msgid "Availabilites tab"
msgstr "Fanen Tilgængelighed"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:193
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Availabilites` tab of the appointment form, time slots can "
"be managed. The target date and time populate as the first time slots."
msgstr ""
"I fanen :guilabel:`Tilgængelighed` i aftaleformularen kan tidslots "
"administreres. Måldato og -tidspunkt udfyldes som de første tidslots."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:196
msgid ""
"To add a new time slot, click :guilabel:`Add a line`. Click into the new "
"blank space under the :guilabel:`From` field, then select and enter the new "
"target start date and time, respectively. Repeat under the new blank space "
"under :guilabel:`To` to select and enter the new target end date and time."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje et nyt tidsslot skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Tilføj en "
"linje`. Klik i den nye tomme plads under feltet :guilabel:`Fra`, og vælg og "
"indtast derefter den nye målstartdato og -tidspunkt. Gentag under den nye "
"tomme plads under :guilabel:`Til` for at vælge og indtaste den nye "
"målslutdato og -tidspunkt."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:206
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Questions` tab, add questions for the attendee to answer "
"when confirming their meeting. Click :guilabel:`Add a line` to configure "
"a :guilabel:`Question`. Then select a :guilabel:`Question Type`, optionally "
"add a :guilabel:`Placeholder` answer, and choose whether it is meeting. "
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` to configure a :guilabel:`Question`. Then "
"select an :guilabel:`Answer Type`, optionally add a "
"placeholder :guilabel:`Answer`, and choose whether it "
"is :guilabel:`Mandatory`."
msgstr ""
"I fanen :guilabel:`Spørgsmål` skal du tilføje spørgsmål, som deltageren skal "
"besvare, når de bekræfter deres møde. Klik på :guilabel:`Tilføj en linje` "
"for at konfigurere et :guilabel:`Spørgsmål`. Vælg derefter "
"en :guilabel:`Spørgsmålstype`, tilføj eventuelt "
"et :guilabel:`Pladsholdersvar`, og vælg, om det er obligatorisk. Klik "
"på :guilabel:`Tilføj en linje` for at konfigurere et :guilabel:`Spørgsmål`. "
"Vælg derefter en :guilabel:`Svartype`, tilføj eventuelt et "
"pladsholder-:guilabel:`Svar`, og vælg, om det er :guilabel:`Obligatorisk`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:213
msgid ""
"To learn how to create more comprehensive questionnaires, head to the "
"**Survey** app documentation on :doc:`creating and configuring data-"
"capturing questions <../marketing/surveys/questions>`."
msgstr ""
"For at lære, hvordan du opretter mere omfattende spørgeskemaer, skal du gå "
"til **Undersøgelser**-appens dokumentation om :doc:`oprettelse og "
"konfiguration af dataindsamlingsspørgsmål <../marketing/surveys/questions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:219
msgid "Communication tab"
msgstr "Kommunikationsfane"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:221
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Introduction Page` field of the :guilabel:`Communication` "
"tab, add additional meeting information to appear on the invitation."
msgstr ""
"I feltet :guilabel:`Introduktionsside` under fanen :guilabel:`Kommunikation` "
"skal du tilføje yderligere mødeinformation, der skal vises på invitationen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:224
msgid ""
"Information added to the :guilabel:`Confirmation Page` field appears once "
"the meeting is confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Information tilføjet til feltet :guilabel:`Bekræftelsesside` vises, når "
"mødet er bekræftet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:226
msgid ""
"Under the *Emails & SMS* heading, click the :guilabel:`Reminders` field to "
"add one or more methods of reminding attendees about the appointment. Under "
"the :guilabel:`Booking Email` field, and :guilabel:`Cancellation Email` "
"field, select an email template to be sent to attendees when booking or "
"cancelling meetings."
msgstr ""
"Under overskriften *E-mails og SMS* skal du klikke på "
"feltet :guilabel:`Påmindelser` for at tilføje en eller flere metoder til at "
"minde deltagere om aftalen. Under feltet :guilabel:`Bookinge-mail` og "
"feltet :guilabel:`Annulleringse-mail` skal du vælge en e-mailskabelon, der "
"skal sendes til deltagere ved booking eller annullering af møder."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:236
msgid "The :guilabel:`Options` tab provides additional configurations:"
msgstr "Fanen :guilabel:`Indstillinger` giver yderligere konfigurationer:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:238
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allow invitations`: Tick the checkbox to allow attendees to "
"invite guests."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tillad invitationer`: Markér afkrydsningsfeltet for at tillade "
"deltagere at invitere gæster."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:239
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Auto Confirm`: Only shown if :guilabel:`Resources` has been "
"selected in the :guilabel:`Availability On` field. Tick the checkbox and "
"enter a maximum percentage of the selected resource(s)' total capacity to "
"create a manual confirmation requirement to finalize the meeting."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Autobekræft`: Vises kun, hvis :guilabel:`Ressourcer` er valgt i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Tilgængelighed på`. Markér afkrydsningsfeltet og indtast "
"en maksimal procentdel af den eller de valgte ressourcers samlede kapacitet "
"for at oprette et manuelt bekræftelseskrav for at færdiggøre mødet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:243
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Display pictures`: Tick the checkbox to display user or resource "
"images across the entire booking flow."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vis billeder`: Markér afkrydsningsfeltet for at vise bruger- "
"eller ressourcebilleder gennem hele bookingforløbet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:245
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Create Opportunity`: When this is selected, each scheduled "
"appointment creates a new **CRM** opportunity."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Opret mulighed`: Når dette er valgt, opretter hver planlagte "
"aftale en ny **CRM**-mulighed."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:247
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Up-front Payment`: Tick the checkbox to require users to pay "
"before confirming their booking. Once this is ticked, a link appears "
"to :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Configure Payment Providers`, which "
"enables online payments."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forudbetaling`: Marker afkrydsningsfeltet for at kræve, at "
"brugere betaler, før de bekræfter deres booking. Når dette er markeret, "
"vises et link til :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Konfigurer "
"betalingsudbydere`, som muliggør onlinebetalinger."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:250
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Website`: Specify which website this meeting invitation will be "
"published on."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Hjemmeside`: Angiv, hvilken hjemmeside denne mødeindkaldelse skal "
"publiceres på."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:251
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Schedule`: Select :guilabel:`Weekly` or :guilabel:`Flexible` "
"scheduling."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Planlægning`: Vælg :guilabel:`Ugentlig` "
"eller :guilabel:`Fleksibel` planlægning."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:252
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allow Bookings`: set a minimum hour window to ensure appointments "
"are confirmed a specified amount of time in advance. For example, set "
"`01:00` to require attendees to confirm at least one hour before their "
"appointment time."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tillad bookinger`: angiv et minimumstidsvindue i timer for at "
"sikre, at aftaler bekræftes et angivet stykke tid i forvejen. Angiv f.eks. "
"`01:00` for at kræve, at deltagere bekræfter mindst en time før deres "
"aftaletidspunkt."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:255
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Cancellation`: set a maximum hour window before the appointment "
"that attendees are able to cancel."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Afbestilling`: angiv et maksimalt tidsvindue i timer før aftalen, "
"inden for hvilket deltagere kan afbestille."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:257
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Timezone`: This defaults to the company's timezone selected in "
"the **Settings** app. To change the timezone, select the desired option from "
"the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tidszone`: Dette er som standard virksomhedens tidszone valgt i "
"**Indstillinger**-appen. For at ændre tidszonen skal du vælge den ønskede "
"mulighed fra rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:3
msgid "Google Calendar synchronization"
msgstr "Google Kalender-synkronisering"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:5
msgid ""
"Synchronize Google Calendar with Odoo to see and manage meetings from both "
"platforms (updates go in both directions). This integration helps organize "
"schedules, so a meeting is never missed."
msgstr ""
"Synkroniser Google Kalender med Odoo for at se og administrere møder fra "
"begge platforme (opdateringer går begge veje). Denne integration hjælper med "
"at organisere tidsplaner, så et møde aldrig bliver overset."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:9
msgid ":doc:`/applications/general/users/google`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/general/users/google`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:10
msgid ":doc:`/applications/general/email_communication/google_oauth`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/general/email_communication/google_oauth`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:13
msgid "Setup in Google"
msgstr "Opsætning i Google"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:16
msgid "Select (or create) a project"
msgstr "Vælg (eller opret) et projekt"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:18
msgid ""
"Create a new Google API project and enable the Google Calendar API. First, "
"go to the `Google API Console <https://console.developers.google.com>`_ and "
"log into the Google account."
msgstr ""
"Opret et nyt Google API-projekt og aktivér Google Kalender API. Gå først til "
"`Google API Console <https://console.developers.google.com>`_ og log ind på "
"Google-kontoen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:22
msgid ""
"If this is the first time visiting this page, Google will prompt the user to "
"enter a country and agree to the Terms of Service. Select a country from the "
"drop-down list and agree to the :abbr:`ToS (Terms of Service)`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis dette er første besøg på denne side, vil Google bede brugeren om at "
"indtaste et land og acceptere servicevilkårene. Vælg et land fra rullemenuen "
"og acceptér :abbr:`ToS (servicevilkår)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:26
msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Select a project` and select (or create) an API "
"project to configure OAuth in, and store credentials. Click :guilabel:`New "
"Project`."
msgstr ""
"Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Vælg et projekt` og vælg (eller opret) et API-"
"projekt, hvor OAuth skal konfigureres, og legitimationsoplysninger gemmes. "
"Klik på :guilabel:`Nyt projekt`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Create a new API project to store credentials."
msgstr "Opret et nyt API-projekt til at gemme legitimationsoplysninger."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:32
msgid ""
"Give the API project a clear name, like `Odoo Sync`, so it can be "
"identified. Then click the :guilabel:`Create` button."
msgstr ""
"Giv API-projektet et klart navn, som f.eks. `Odoo Sync`, så det kan "
"identificeres. Klik derefter på knappen :guilabel:`Opret`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:36
msgid "Enable Google calendar API"
msgstr "Aktivér Google calendar API"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:38
msgid ""
"Now, click on :guilabel:`Enabled APIs and Services` in the left menu. "
"Select :guilabel:`Enabled APIs and Services` again if the :guilabel:`Search "
"bar` does not appear."
msgstr ""
"Klik nu på :guilabel:`Aktiverede API'er og tjenester` i venstre menu. "
"Vælg :guilabel:`Aktiverede API'er og tjenester` igen, "
"hvis :guilabel:`Søgelinjen` ikke vises."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Enable APIs and Services on the API Project."
msgstr "Aktivér API'er og tjenester på API-projektet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:44
msgid ""
"After that, search for `Google Calendar API` using the search bar and "
"select :guilabel:`Google Calendar API` from the search results. "
"Click :guilabel:`Enable`."
msgstr ""
"Søg derefter efter `Google Calendar API` ved hjælp af søgelinjen og "
"vælg :guilabel:`Google Calendar API` fra søgeresultaterne. Klik "
"på :guilabel:`Aktivér`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Enable the Google Calendar API."
msgstr "Aktivér Google Calendar API."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:51
msgid "OAuth consent screen"
msgstr "OAuth-samtykkeskærm"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:53
msgid ""
"Now that the API project has been created, OAuth should be configured. To do "
"that, click on :guilabel:`OAuth consent screen` in the left menu, then click "
"the :guilabel:`Get started` button."
msgstr ""
"Nu hvor API-projektet er oprettet, skal OAuth konfigureres. Klik "
"på :guilabel:`OAuth-samtykkeskærm` i venstre menu og klik derefter på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Kom i gang`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:57
msgid ""
"*Personal* Gmail Accounts are only allowed to be **External** User Type, "
"which means Google may require an approval, or for *Scopes* to be added on. "
"However, using a *Google WorkSpace* account allows for **Internal** User "
"Type to be used."
msgstr ""
"*Personlige* Gmail-konti må kun være **Eksterne** brugertyper, hvilket "
"betyder, at Google muligvis kræver godkendelse eller tilføjelse af *scopes*. "
"Brug af en *Google WorkSpace*-konto tillader dog, at **Intern** brugertype "
"bruges."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:61
msgid ""
"Note, as well, that while the API connection is in the *External* testing "
"mode, then no approval is necessary from Google. User limits in this testing "
"mode is set to 100 users."
msgstr ""
"Bemærk også, at mens API-forbindelsen er i *ekstern* testtilstand, er der "
"ingen godkendelse nødvendig fra Google. Brugergrænsen i denne testtilstand "
"er sat til 100 brugere."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:64
msgid "Follow the proceeding steps, in order:"
msgstr "Følg de efterfølgende trin i rækkefølge:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:66
msgid ""
"In :guilabel:`App Information`, type `Odoo` in the :guilabel:`App name` "
"field, then enter the email address for the :guilabel:`User support email` "
"field and click the :guilabel:`Next` button."
msgstr ""
"I :guilabel:`App Information` skal du skrive `Odoo` i feltet :guilabel:`App "
"name`, derefter indtaste e-mailadressen i feltet :guilabel:`User support "
"email` og klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Next`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:68
msgid ""
"In :guilabel:`Audience`, select :guilabel:`External`, then click "
"the :guilabel:`Next` button."
msgstr ""
"I :guilabel:`Audience` skal du vælge :guilabel:`External` og derefter klikke "
"på knappen :guilabel:`Next`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:69
msgid ""
"In :guilabel:`Contact Information`, enter the email again, then click "
"the :guilabel:`Next` button."
msgstr ""
"I :guilabel:`Contact Information` skal du indtaste e-mailen igen og derefter "
"klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Next`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:71
msgid ""
"In :guilabel:`Finish`, tick the checkbox to agree to :guilabel:`Google API "
"Services: User Policy.` For the last step, click the :guilabel:`Create` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"I :guilabel:`Finish` skal du markere afkrydsningsfeltet for at "
"acceptere :guilabel:`Google API Services: User Policy.` Som sidste trin skal "
"du klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Create`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:75
msgid "Authorized domain setup"
msgstr "Opsætning af autoriseret domæne"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:77
msgid ""
"Next, any domains set to appear on the consent screen or in an OAuth "
"client's configuration must be pre-registered. To do so, navigate "
"to :guilabel:`Branding` in the left menu. In the :guilabel:`Authorized "
"domains` section, click the :guilabel:`Add domain` button to create a field "
"to enter an authorized domain. Enter a domain, such as `odoo.com`, then "
"click the :guilabel:`Save` button at the bottom of the page."
msgstr ""
"Derefter skal alle domæner, der er indstillet til at vises på "
"samtykkeskærmen eller i en OAuth-klients konfiguration, være præ-"
"registreret. For at gøre dette skal du navigere til :guilabel:`Branding` i "
"menuen til venstre. I afsnittet :guilabel:`Authorized domains` skal du "
"klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Add domain` for at oprette et felt til at "
"indtaste et autoriseret domæne. Indtast et domæne, såsom `odoo.com`, og klik "
"derefter på knappen :guilabel:`Save` nederst på siden."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:84
msgid "Test users"
msgstr "Testbrugere"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:86
msgid ""
"To give users the ability to sync with personal Gmail accounts, they must be "
"set as a test user. Setup test users by going to :guilabel:`Audience` in the "
"left-side menu and clicking the :guilabel:`Add users` button in "
"the :guilabel:`Test users` section. Enter any desired user emails, and click "
"the :guilabel:`Save` button."
msgstr ""
"For at give brugere mulighed for at synkronisere med personlige Gmail-konti "
"skal de oprettes som testbrugere. Opsæt testbrugere ved at gå "
"til :guilabel:`Audience` i menuen til venstre og klikke på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Add users` i afsnittet :guilabel:`Test users`. Indtast de "
"ønskede bruger-e-mails og klik på knappen :guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:92
msgid "Create credentials"
msgstr "Opret legitimationsoplysninger"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:94
msgid ""
"The *Client ID* and the *Client Secret* are both needed to connect Google "
"Calendar to Odoo. This is the last step in the Google console. Begin by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Clients` in the left menu. Then, click :guilabel:`Create "
"Credentials`, and select :guilabel:`OAuth client ID`, Google will open a "
"guide to create credentials."
msgstr ""
"*Client ID* og *Client Secret* er begge nødvendige for at forbinde Google "
"Calendar til Odoo. Dette er det sidste trin i Google-konsollen. Begynd med "
"at klikke på :guilabel:`Clients` i menuen til venstre. Klik derefter "
"på :guilabel:`Create Credentials` og vælg :guilabel:`OAuth client ID`. "
"Google vil åbne en guide til at oprette legitimationsoplysninger."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:99
msgid ""
"Under :menuselection:`Create OAuth Client ID`, select :guilabel:`Website "
"application` for the :guilabel:`Application Type` field, and type `My Odoo "
"Database` for the :guilabel:`Name`."
msgstr ""
"Under :menuselection:`Create OAuth Client ID` skal du "
"vælge :guilabel:`Website application` for feltet :guilabel:`Application "
"Type` og skrive `My Odoo Database` i feltet :guilabel:`Name`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:102
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Authorized JavaScript Origins` section, "
"click :guilabel:`+ Add URI` and type the company's Odoo full :abbr:`URL "
"(Uniform Resource Locator)` address."
msgstr ""
"Under afsnittet :guilabel:`Authorized JavaScript Origins` skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`+ Add URI` og indtaste virksomhedens komplette Odoo :abbr:`URL "
"(Uniform Resource Locator)`-adresse."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:106
msgid ""
"When entering the *Authorized JavaScript Origins*, the exact URL of the Odoo "
"database must be used."
msgstr ""
"Når du indtaster *Authorized JavaScript Origins*, skal den præcise URL for "
"Odoo-databasen bruges."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:109
msgid ""
"If the database is accessible through both an `.odoo.com` subdomain and a "
"custom domain, the custom domain configured as the primary domain should be "
"used. The `.odoo.com` subdomain may not work correctly in all cases and can "
"result in authentication errors."
msgstr ""
"Hvis databasen er tilgængelig via både et `.odoo.com`-subdomæne og et "
"brugerdefineret domæne, skal det brugerdefinerede domæne, der er "
"konfigureret som det primære domæne, bruges. `.odoo.com`-subdomænet fungerer "
"muligvis ikke korrekt i alle tilfælde og kan resultere i godkendelsesfejl."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:113
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Authorized redirect URIs` section, click :guilabel:`+ "
"Add URI` and type the company's Odoo :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)` "
"address followed by `/google_account/authentication`. Finally, "
"click :guilabel:`Create`."
msgstr ""
"Under afsnittet :guilabel:`Authorized redirect URIs` skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`+ Add URI` og indtaste virksomhedens Odoo :abbr:`URL (Uniform "
"Resource Locator)`-adresse efterfulgt af `/google_account/authentication`. "
"Klik til sidst på :guilabel:`Create`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Add the authorized JavaScript origins and the authorized redirect URIs."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj de autoriserede JavaScript-origins og de autoriserede redirect-URI'er."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:120
msgid ""
"A :guilabel:`Client ID` and :guilabel:`Client Secret` will appear, save "
"these somewhere safe."
msgstr ""
"Et :guilabel:`Client ID` og en :guilabel:`Client Secret` vil blive vist. Gem "
"disse et sikkert sted."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:123
msgid "Setup in Odoo"
msgstr "Opsætning i Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:125
msgid ""
"Once the *Client ID* and the *Client Secret* are located, open the Odoo "
"database and go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Calendar` to find "
"the :guilabel:`Google Calendar` feature. Tick the checkbox "
"labeled :guilabel:`Google Calendar`."
msgstr ""
"Når *Client ID* og *Client Secret* er fundet, skal du åbne Odoo-databasen og "
"gå til :menuselection:`Settings --> Calendar` for at finde "
"funktionen :guilabel:`Google Calendar`. Markér afkrydsningsfeltet med "
"titlen :guilabel:`Google Calendar`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "The Google Calendar checkbox in General Settings."
msgstr "Afkrydsningsfeltet Google Calendar i generelle indstillinger."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:132
msgid ""
"Next, copy and paste the *Client ID* and the *Client Secret* from the Google "
"Calendar API credentials page into their respective fields below "
"the :guilabel:`Google Calendar` checkbox. Then, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Kopiér og indsæt derefter *Client ID* og *Client Secret* fra Google Calendar "
"API-legitimationssiden i deres respektive felter under "
"afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Google Calendar`. Klik derefter "
"på :guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:137
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`Pause Synchronization` checkbox to temporarily pause "
"events from being updated. This allows for testing and troubleshooting "
"without removing credentials or uninstalling the synchronization. To resume "
"the sync, clear the checkbox and save."
msgstr ""
"Markér afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Pause Synchronization` for midlertidigt "
"at sætte opdatering af begivenheder på pause. Dette giver mulighed for test "
"og fejlfinding uden at fjerne legitimationsoplysninger eller afinstallere "
"synkroniseringen. For at genoptage synkroniseringen skal du fjerne "
"markeringen i afkrydsningsfeltet og gemme."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:142
msgid "Sync calendar in Odoo"
msgstr "Synkroniser kalender i Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:144
msgid ""
"Finally, open the :menuselection:`Calendar` app in Odoo and click "
"the :guilabel:`Google` sync button to sync Google Calendar with Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Til sidst skal du åbne :menuselection:`Kalender`-appen i Odoo og klikke på "
"synkroniseringsknappen :guilabel:`Google` for at synkronisere Google "
"Kalender med Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid ""
"Click the Google sync button in Odoo Calendar to sync Google Calendar with "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Klik på Google-synkroniseringsknappen i Odoo Kalender for at synkronisere "
"Google Kalender med Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:151
msgid ""
"When syncing Google Calendar with Odoo for the first time, the page will "
"redirect to the Google Account. From there, select the :guilabel:`Email "
"Account` that should have access, then select :guilabel:`Continue` (should "
"the app be unverified), and finally select :guilabel:`Continue` (to give "
"permission for the transfer of data)."
msgstr ""
"Når Google Kalender synkroniseres med Odoo for første gang, vil siden "
"omdirigere til Google-kontoen. Derfra skal du vælge :guilabel:`E-mailkonto`, "
"som skal have adgang, derefter vælge :guilabel:`Fortsæt` (hvis appen er "
"ubekræftet), og endelig vælge :guilabel:`Fortsæt` (for at give tilladelse "
"til overførsel af data)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Give Odoo permission to access Google Calendar."
msgstr "Giv Odoo tilladelse til at få adgang til Google Kalender."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:159
msgid "Now, Odoo Calendar is successfully synced with Google Calendar!"
msgstr "Nu er Odoo Kalender succesfuldt synkroniseret med Google Kalender!"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:162
msgid ""
"Odoo highly recommends testing the Google calendar synchronization on a test "
"database and a test email address (that is not used for any other purpose) "
"before attempting to sync the desired Google Calendar with the user's "
"production database."
msgstr ""
"Odoo anbefaler kraftigt at teste Google-kalendersynkroniseringen på en "
"testdatabase og en test-e-mailadresse (som ikke bruges til andre formål), "
"før du forsøger at synkronisere den ønskede Google Kalender med brugerens "
"produktionsdatabase."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:166
msgid "Once a user synchronizes their Google calendar with the Odoo calendar:"
msgstr "Når en bruger synkroniserer sin Google-kalender med Odoo-kalenderen:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:168
msgid ""
"Creating an event in Odoo causes Google to send an invitation to all event "
"attendees."
msgstr ""
"Oprettelse af et arrangement i Odoo får Google til at sende en invitation "
"til alle deltagere i arrangementet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:169
msgid ""
"Deleting an event in Odoo causes Google to send a cancellation to all event "
"attendees."
msgstr ""
"Sletning af et arrangement i Odoo får Google til at sende en aflysning til "
"alle deltagere i arrangementet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:170
msgid ""
"Adding a contact to an event causes Google to send an invitation to all "
"event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Tilføjelse af en kontakt til et arrangement får Google til at sende en "
"invitation til alle deltagere i arrangementet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:171
msgid ""
"Removing a contact from an event causes Google to send a cancellation to all "
"event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Fjernelse af en kontakt fra et arrangement får Google til at sende en "
"aflysning til alle deltagere i arrangementet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:173
msgid ""
"Events can be created in *Google Calendar* without sending a notification by "
"selecting :guilabel:`Don't Send` when prompted to send invitation emails."
msgstr ""
"Arrangementer kan oprettes i *Google Kalender* uden at sende en meddelelse "
"ved at vælge :guilabel:`Send ikke`, når du bliver bedt om at sende "
"invitations-e-mails."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:177
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:210
msgid "Troubleshoot sync"
msgstr "Fejlfind synkronisering"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:179
msgid ""
"There may be times when the *Google Calendar* account does not sync "
"correctly with Odoo. Sync issues can be seen in the database logs."
msgstr ""
"Der kan være tidspunkter, hvor *Google Kalender*-kontoen ikke synkroniserer "
"korrekt med Odoo. Synkroniseringsproblemer kan ses i databaseloggene."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:182
msgid ""
"In these cases, the account needs troubleshooting. A reset can be performed "
"using the :guilabel:`Reset Account` button, which can be accessed by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Manage Users`. Then, select "
"the user to modify the calendar, and click the :guilabel:`Calendar` tab."
msgstr ""
"I disse tilfælde skal kontoen fejlfindes. En nulstilling kan udføres ved "
"hjælp af knappen :guilabel:`Nulstil konto`, som kan tilgås ved at navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Indstillinger-appen --> Administrer brugere`. Vælg "
"derefter brugeren for at ændre kalenderen, og klik på "
"fanen :guilabel:`Kalender`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "Reset buttons highlighted on the calendar tab of the user."
msgstr "Nulstillingsknapper fremhævet på kalenderfanen for brugeren."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:190
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:224
msgid "Next, click :guilabel:`Reset Account` under the correct calendar."
msgstr ""
"Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Nulstil konto` under den korrekte kalender."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:193
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:227
msgid "Reset options"
msgstr "Nulstillingsmuligheder"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:195
msgid ""
"The following reset options are available for troubleshooting Google "
"calendar sync with Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"Følgende nulstillingsmuligheder er tilgængelige til fejlfinding af Google-"
"kalendersynkronisering med Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Google calendar reset options in Odoo."
msgstr "Google-kalendernulstillingsmuligheder i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:200
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:236
msgid ":guilabel:`User's Existing Events`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Brugerens eksisterende arrangementer`:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:202
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:238
msgid ":guilabel:`Leave them untouched`: no changes to the events."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Lad dem være uændrede`: ingen ændringer af arrangementerne."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:203
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delete from the current Google Calendar account`: delete the "
"events from *Google Calendar*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Slet fra den aktuelle Google Kalender-konto`: slet "
"arrangementerne fra *Google Kalender*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:205
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:241
msgid ":guilabel:`Delete from Odoo`: delete the events from the Odoo calendar."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Slet fra Odoo`: slet arrangementerne fra Odoo-kalenderen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:206
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delete from both`: delete the events from both *Google Calendar* "
"and Odoo calendar."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Slet fra begge`: slet arrangementerne fra både *Google Kalender* "
"og Odoo-kalenderen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:208
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:245
msgid ":guilabel:`Next Synchronization`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Næste synkronisering`:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:210
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Synchronize only new events`: sync new events on *Google "
"Calendar* and/or Odoo calendar."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Synkroniser kun nye arrangementer`: synkroniser nye arrangementer "
"på *Google Kalender* og/eller Odoo-kalenderen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:212
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Synchronize all existing events`: sync all events on *Google "
"Calendar* and/or Odoo calendar."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Synkroniser alle eksisterende arrangementer`: synkroniser alle "
"arrangementer på *Google Kalender* og/eller Odoo-kalenderen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:215
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:252
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm` after making the selection to modify the user's "
"events and the calendar synchronization."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Bekræft` efter valget for at ændre brugerens "
"arrangementer og kalendersynkroniseringen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:219
msgid "Google OAuth FAQ"
msgstr "Google OAuth FAQ"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:221
msgid ""
"At times there can be configuration errors that occur, and troubleshooting "
"is needed to resolve the issue. Below are the most common errors that may "
"occur when configuring the *Google Calendar* for use with Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Til tider kan der opstå konfigurationsfejl, som kræver fejlfinding for at "
"løse problemet. Nedenfor er de mest almindelige fejl, der kan opstå ved "
"konfiguration af *Google Kalender* til brug med Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:226
msgid "Production vs. testing publishing status"
msgstr "Publicering i produktion vs. test"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:228
msgid ""
"Choosing :guilabel:`Production` as the :guilabel:`Publishing Status` "
"(instead of :guilabel:`Testing`) displays the following warning message:"
msgstr ""
"Valg af :guilabel:`Produktion` som :guilabel:`Publiceringsstatus` (i stedet "
"for :guilabel:`Test`) viser følgende advarselsmeddelelse:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:231
msgid ""
"`OAuth is limited to 100 sensitive scope logins until the OAuth consent "
"screen is verified. This may require a verification process that can take "
"several days.`"
msgstr ""
"`OAuth er begrænset til 100 følsomme scope-logins, indtil OAuth-"
"samtykkeskærmen er verificeret. Dette kan kræve en verificeringsproces, der "
"kan tage flere dage.`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:234
msgid ""
"To correct this warning, navigate to the `Google API Platform <https://"
"console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials/consent>`_. If "
"the :guilabel:`Publishing Status` is :guilabel:`In Production`, "
"click :guilabel:`Back to Testing` to correct the issue."
msgstr ""
"For at rette denne advarsel skal du navigere til `Google API Platform "
"<https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials/consent>`_. "
"Hvis :guilabel:`Publiceringsstatus` er :guilabel:`I produktion`, skal du "
"klikke på :guilabel:`Tilbage til test` for at rette problemet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:239
msgid "No test users added"
msgstr "Ingen testbrugere tilføjet"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:241
msgid ""
"If no test users are added to the :guilabel:`OAuth consent screen`, then "
"an :guilabel:`Error 403: access_denied` populates."
msgstr ""
"Hvis ingen testbrugere er tilføjet til :guilabel:`OAuth-samtykkeskærmen`, "
"vises en :guilabel:`Fejl 403: access_denied`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "403 Access Denied Error."
msgstr "403 adgang nægtet-fejl."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:247
msgid ""
"To correct this error, return to the :guilabel:`OAuth consent screen`, "
"under :guilabel:`APIs & Services`, and add test users to the app. Add the "
"email to be configured in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"For at rette denne fejl skal du vende tilbage til :guilabel:`OAuth-"
"samtykkeskærmen` under :guilabel:`APIs & Services` og tilføje testbrugere "
"til appen. Tilføj den e-mail, der skal konfigureres i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:251
msgid "Application Type"
msgstr "Applikationstype"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:253
msgid ""
"When creating the credentials (OAuth *Client ID* and *Client Secret*), "
"if :guilabel:`Desktop App` is selected for the :guilabel:`Application Type`, "
"an :guilabel:`Authorization Error` appears (:guilabel:`Error "
"400:redirect_uri_mismatch`)."
msgstr ""
"Når der oprettes legitimationsoplysninger (OAuth *Client ID* og *Client "
"Secret*), hvis :guilabel:`Desktop App` er valgt for :guilabel:`Application "
"Type`, vises en :guilabel:`Authorization Error` (:guilabel:`Error "
"400:redirect_uri_mismatch`)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Error 400 Redirect URI Mismatch."
msgstr "Fejl 400 Redirect URI stemmer ikke overens."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:260
msgid ""
"To correct this error, delete the existing credentials, and create new "
"credentials, by selecting :guilabel:`Web Application` for "
"the :guilabel:`Application Type`."
msgstr ""
"For at rette denne fejl skal du slette de eksisterende "
"legitimationsoplysninger og oprette nye legitimationsoplysninger ved at "
"vælge :guilabel:`Web Application` for :guilabel:`Application Type`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:263
msgid ""
"Then, under :guilabel:`Authorized redirect URIs`, click :guilabel:`ADD URI`, "
"and type: `https://yourdbname.odoo.com/google_account/authentication` in the "
"field, being sure to replace *yourdbname* in the URL with the **real** Odoo "
"database name."
msgstr ""
"Under :guilabel:`Authorized redirect URIs` skal du derefter klikke "
"på :guilabel:`ADD URI` og skrive: `https://yourdbname.odoo.com/"
"google_account/authentication` i feltet. Sørg for at erstatte *yourdbname* i "
"URL'en med det **rigtige** Odoo database-navn."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:268
msgid ""
"Ensure that the domain (used in the URI: `https://yourdbname.odoo.com/"
"google_account/authentication`) is the exact same domain as configured in "
"the `web.base.url` system parameter."
msgstr ""
"Sørg for, at domænet (brugt i URI'en: `https://yourdbname.odoo.com/"
"google_account/authentication`) er nøjagtig det samme domæne som "
"konfigureret i systemparameteren `web.base.url`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:272
msgid ""
"Access the `web.base.url` by activating :ref:`developer mode <developer-"
"mode>`, and navigating to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical header "
"menu --> Parameters section --> System Parameters`."
msgstr ""
"Få adgang til `web.base.url` ved at aktivere :ref:`udviklertilstand "
"<developer-mode>` og navigere til :menuselection:`Indstillinger --> Teknisk "
"overskriftsmenu --> Parameters-sektion --> System Parameters`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:3
msgid "Outlook Calendar synchronization"
msgstr "Synkronisering af Outlook Kalender"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:5
msgid ""
"Synchronizing a user's *Outlook Calendar* with Odoo is useful for keeping "
"track of tasks and appointments across all related applications."
msgstr ""
"Synkronisering af en brugers *Outlook Kalender* med Odoo er nyttigt til at "
"holde styr på opgaver og aftaler på tværs af alle relaterede applikationer."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:9
msgid ":doc:`../../general/users/azure`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../general/users/azure`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:10
msgid ":doc:`../../general/email_communication/azure_oauth`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../general/email_communication/azure_oauth`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:13
msgid "Microsoft Azure setup"
msgstr "Opsætning af Microsoft Azure"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:15
msgid ""
"To sync the *Outlook Calendar* with Odoo's *Calendar*, a Microsoft *Azure* "
"account is required. Creating an account is free for users who have never "
"tried, or paid for, *Azure*. For more information, view the account options "
"on the `Azure website <https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/free/?"
"WT.mc_id=A261C142F>`_."
msgstr ""
"For at synkronisere *Outlook Kalender* med Odoo's *Kalender* kræves en "
"Microsoft *Azure*-konto. Oprettelse af en konto er gratis for brugere, der "
"aldrig har prøvet eller betalt for *Azure*. For mere information, se "
"kontomulighederne på `Azure-hjemmesiden <https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/"
"free/?WT.mc_id=A261C142F>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:20
msgid ""
"Refer to `Microsoft's documentation <https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/"
"active-directory/ develop/quickstart-create-new-tenant>`_ on how to set up a "
"Microsoft *Entra ID* (formally called Microsoft *Azure Active Directory "
"(Azure AD)*). This is an API console to manage and register Microsoft "
"applications."
msgstr ""
"Se `Microsofts dokumentation <https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/active-"
"directory/ develop/quickstart-create-new-tenant>`_ om, hvordan du opsætter "
"en Microsoft *Entra ID* (tidligere kaldet Microsoft *Azure Active Directory "
"(Azure AD)*). Dette er en API-konsol til at administrere og registrere "
"Microsoft-applikationer."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:25
msgid ""
"Existing Microsoft *Entra ID* users should log in at the `Microsoft Azure "
"developer portal <https://portal.azure.com/#home>`_. Next, "
"select :guilabel:`View` under the section labeled :guilabel:`Manage "
"Microsoft Entra ID`."
msgstr ""
"Eksisterende Microsoft *Entra ID*-brugere skal logge ind på `Microsoft Azure-"
"udviklerportalen <https://portal.azure.com/#home>`_. Vælg "
"derefter :guilabel:`View` under sektionen med navnet :guilabel:`Manage "
"Microsoft Entra ID`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:30
msgid "Register application"
msgstr "Registrer applikation"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:32
msgid ""
"After logging in with the Microsoft *Entra ID*, `register an application "
"<https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/active-directory/develop/quickstart-"
"register-app>`_."
msgstr ""
"Efter login med Microsoft *Entra ID*, `registrer en applikation <https://"
"docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/active-directory/develop/quickstart-register-"
"app>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:35
msgid ""
"To create an application, click :guilabel:`+ Add` in the top menu. From the "
"resulting drop-down menu, select :guilabel:`App Registration`."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en applikation skal du klikke på :guilabel:`+ Add` i "
"topmenuen. Fra den resulterende rullemenu skal du vælge :guilabel:`App "
"Registration`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid ""
"Microsoft Azure management page with + Add and App Registration menu "
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Microsoft Azure administrationssiden med + Add og App Registration-menuen "
"fremhævet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:42
msgid "Enter a unique :guilabel:`Name` for the connected application."
msgstr "Indtast et unikt :guilabel:`Name` for den forbundne applikation."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:44
msgid ""
"Choosing the appropriate :guilabel:`Supported account type` is essential, or "
"else the connected application will not work. Users who wish to connect "
"their *Outlook Calendar* to Odoo should select the :guilabel:`Accounts in "
"any organizational directory (Any Microsoft Entra ID directory - "
"Multitenant) and personal Microsoft accounts (e.g. Skype, Xbox)` option "
"for :guilabel:`Supported account types`."
msgstr ""
"Valg af den passende :guilabel:`Supported account type` er afgørende, ellers "
"vil den forbundne applikation ikke fungere. Brugere, der ønsker at forbinde "
"deres *Outlook Kalender* til Odoo, skal vælge "
"indstillingen :guilabel:`Accounts in any organizational directory (Any "
"Microsoft Entra ID directory - Multitenant) and personal Microsoft accounts "
"(e.g. Skype, Xbox)` for :guilabel:`Supported account types`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:50
msgid ""
"When configuring the :guilabel:`Redirect URI`, choose the :guilabel:`Web` "
"option from the first drop-down menu. Then, enter the Odoo database URI "
"(URL) followed by `/microsoft_account/authentication`."
msgstr ""
"Při konfiguraci :guilabel:`URI přesměrování` vyberte z první rozevírací "
"nabídky možnost :guilabel:`Web`. Poté zadejte URI (URL) Odoo databáze "
"následované `/microsoft_account/authentication`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:55
msgid ""
"Enter `https://yourdbname.odoo.com/microsoft_account/authentication` for "
"the :guilabel:`Redirect URI`. Replace `yourdbname.odoo.com` with "
"the :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)`."
msgstr ""
"Zadejte `https://yourdbname.odoo.com/microsoft_account/authentication` "
"jako :guilabel:`URI přesměrování`. Nahraďte `yourdbname.odoo.com` :abbr:`URL "
"(Uniform Resource Locator)` vaší databáze."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:59
msgid ""
"Ensure the database's :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)` (domain) used "
"in the URI is the exact same domain as the one configured on the "
"`web.base.url` system parameter."
msgstr ""
"Ujistěte se, že :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)` (doména) databáze "
"použitá v URI je přesně stejná doména jako ta nakonfigurovaná v systémovém "
"parametru `web.base.url`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:62
msgid ""
"Access the `web.base.url` by activating :ref:`developer mode <developer-"
"mode>`, and navigating to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical header "
"menu --> Parameters section --> System Parameters`. Then, select it from "
"the :guilabel:`Key` list on the :guilabel:`System Parameters` page."
msgstr ""
"Přístup k `web.base.url` získáte aktivací :ref:`režimu pro vývojáře "
"<developer-mode>` a přechodem do :menuselection:`Nastavení --> Technické "
"menu --> Parametry --> Systémové parametry`. Poté jej vyberte ze "
"seznamu :guilabel:`Klíč` na stránce :guilabel:`Systémové parametry`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid ""
"The \"Supported account type\" and \"Redirect URI\" settings in the "
"Microsoft Entra ID portal."
msgstr ""
"Nastavení „Podporovaný typ účtu\" a „URI přesměrování\" na portálu Microsoft "
"Entra ID."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:71
msgid ""
"For more information on the restrictions and limitations of URIs, check "
"Microsoft's `Redirect URI (reply URL) restrictions and limitations <https://"
"docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/active-directory/develop/reply-url>`_ page."
msgstr ""
"Více informací o omezeních URI naleznete na stránce Microsoftu <https://"
"docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/active-directory/develop/reply-url>."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:75
msgid ""
"Finally, on the application registration page, click :guilabel:`Register` "
"button to complete the application registration. The :guilabel:`Application "
"(client) ID` is produced. Copy this value, as it is needed later, in "
"the :ref:`outlook_calendar/odoo_setup`."
msgstr ""
"Nakonec na stránce registrace aplikace klikněte na "
"tlačítko :guilabel:`Registrovat`, čímž dokončíte registraci aplikace. "
"Vytvoří se :guilabel:`ID aplikace (klienta)`. Zkopírujte tuto hodnotu, "
"protože ji budete potřebovat později v :ref:`outlook_calendar/odoo_setup`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid ""
"Application client ID highlighted in the essentials section of the newly "
"created\n"
"application."
msgstr ""
"ID klienta aplikace zvýrazněné v základní sekci nově vytvořené aplikace."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:85
msgid "Create client secret"
msgstr "Vytvořit tajný klíč klienta"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:87
msgid ""
"The second credential needed to complete the synchronization of the "
"Microsoft *Outlook Calendar* is the *Client Secret*. The user **must** add a "
"client secret, as this allows Odoo to authenticate itself, requiring no "
"interaction from the user's side. *Certificates* are optional."
msgstr ""
"Druhým přihlašovacím údajem potřebným k dokončení synchronizace s Microsoft "
"*Outlook kalendářem* je *tajný klíč klienta*. Uživatel **musí** přidat tajný "
"klíč klienta, protože to umožňuje Odoo autentizovat se bez interakce ze "
"strany uživatele. *Certifikáty* jsou volitelné."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:91
msgid ""
"To add a client secret, click :menuselection:`Certificates & secrets` in the "
"left menu. Then click :guilabel:`+ New client secret` to create the client "
"secret."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li přidat tajný klíč klienta, klikněte v levé nabídce "
"na :menuselection:`Certifikáty a tajné klíče`. Poté klikněte na :guilabel:`+ "
"Nový tajný klíč klienta`, čímž tajný klíč vytvoříte."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid ""
"New client secret page with certificates and secrets menu and new client "
"secret option\n"
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Stránka nového tajného klíče klienta se zvýrazněnou nabídkou certifikátů a "
"tajných klíčů a možností nového tajného klíče klienta."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:99
msgid ""
"Next, type a :guilabel:`Description`, and select when the client "
"secret :guilabel:`Expires`. Available options include: :guilabel:`90 days (3 "
"months)`, :guilabel:`365 days (12 months)`, :guilabel:`545 days (18 "
"months)`, :guilabel:`730 days (24 months)` or :guilabel:`Custom`. "
"The :guilabel:`Custom` option allows the administrator to set "
"a :guilabel:`Start` and :guilabel:`End` date."
msgstr ""
"Dále zadejte :guilabel:`Popis` a vyberte, kdy tajný klíč "
"klienta :guilabel:`vyprší`. Dostupné možnosti zahrnují: :guilabel:`90 dní (3 "
"měsíce)`, :guilabel:`365 dní (12 měsíců)`, :guilabel:`545 dní (18 "
"měsíců)`, :guilabel:`730 dní (24 měsíců)` nebo :guilabel:`Vlastní`. "
"Možnost :guilabel:`Vlastní` umožňuje správci nastavit "
"datum :guilabel:`začátku` a :guilabel:`konce`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:105
msgid "Finally, click :guilabel:`Add` to :guilabel:`Add a client secret`."
msgstr ""
"Nakonec klikněte na :guilabel:`Přidat`, čímž :guilabel:`přidáte tajný klíč "
"klienta`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:108
msgid ""
"Since resetting the synchronization can be tricky, Odoo recommends setting "
"the maximum allowed expiration date for the client secret (24 months or "
"custom), so there is no need to re-synchronize soon."
msgstr ""
"Vzhledem k tomu, že obnovení synchronizace může být složité, Odoo doporučuje "
"nastavit maximální povolenou dobu vypršení platnosti tajného klíče klienta "
"(24 měsíců nebo vlastní), aby nebylo nutné brzy provádět opětovnou "
"synchronizaci."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:112
msgid "Copy the :guilabel:`Value` for use in the next section."
msgstr "Zkopírujte :guilabel:`hodnotu` pro použití v další sekci."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:115
msgid ""
"Client secret values cannot be viewed, except immediately after creation. Be "
"sure to save the secret when created *before* leaving the page."
msgstr ""
"Hodnoty tajných klíčů klienta nelze zobrazit, kromě okamžiku bezprostředně "
"po vytvoření. Nezapomeňte tajný klíč uložit při jeho vytvoření, *než* "
"stránku opustíte."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:121
msgid "Configuration in Odoo"
msgstr "Konfigurace v Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:123
msgid ""
"In the Odoo database, go to :menuselection:`Calendar app --> Configuration --"
"> Settings`, and tick the checkbox beside the :guilabel:`Outlook Calendar` "
"setting. Remember to click :guilabel:`Save` to implement the changes."
msgstr ""
"V databázi Odoo přejděte do :menuselection:`Kalender --> Konfigurace --> "
"Nastavení` a zaškrtněte políčko u nastavení :guilabel:`Outlook kalendář`. "
"Nezapomeňte kliknout na :guilabel:`Uložit`, abyste změny implementovali."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "The \"Outlook Calendar\" setting activated in Odoo."
msgstr "Nastavení „Outlook kalendář\" aktivované v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:130
msgid ""
"From the Microsoft *Azure* portal, under the :guilabel:`Overview` section of "
"the application, copy the :guilabel:`Application (Client) ID`, if it has not "
"already been copied, and paste it into the :guilabel:`Client ID` field in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Fra Microsoft *Azure*-portalen, under sektionen :guilabel:`Oversigt` i "
"applikationen, kopiér :guilabel:`Program-id (klient)`, hvis det ikke "
"allerede er kopieret, og indsæt det i feltet :guilabel:`Klient-id` i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "The \"Client ID\" in the Microsoft Azure portal."
msgstr "\"Klient-id\" i Microsoft Azure-portalen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:138
msgid ""
"Copy the previously-acquired :guilabel:`Value` (Client Secret Value), and "
"paste it into the :guilabel:`Client Secret` field in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Kopiér den tidligere hentede :guilabel:`Værdi` (klienthemmelighedsværdi), og "
"indsæt den i feltet :guilabel:`Klienthemmelighed` i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "The \"Client Secret\" token to be copied from Microsoft to Odoo."
msgstr ""
"\"Klienthemmelighed\"-tokenet, der skal kopieres fra Microsoft til Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:145
msgid ""
"Finally, on the Odoo :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings` page, "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Til sidst, på Odoo-siden :menuselection:`Indstillinger --> Generelle "
"indstillinger`, klik på :guilabel:`Gem`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:150
msgid "Sync with Outlook"
msgstr "Synkronisér med Outlook"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:154
msgid ""
"Odoo highly recommends testing the Outlook calendar synchronization on a "
"test database and a test email address (that is not used for any other "
"purpose) before attempting to sync the desired Outlook Calendar with the "
"user's production database."
msgstr ""
"Odoo anbefaler stærkt at teste Outlook-kalendersynkroniseringen på en "
"testdatabase og en teste-mailadresse (som ikke bruges til andre formål), før "
"der forsøges at synkronisere den ønskede Outlook-kalender med brugerens "
"produktionsdatabase."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:158
msgid ""
"If the user has any past, present, or future events on their Odoo calendar "
"before syncing their Outlook calendar, Outlook will treat the events pulled "
"from Odoo's calendar during the sync as new events, causing an email "
"notification to be sent from Outlook to all the event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Hvis brugeren har tidligere, nuværende eller fremtidige arrangementer i "
"deres Odoo-kalender, før Outlook-kalenderen synkroniseres, vil Outlook "
"behandle arrangementerne hentet fra Odoo's kalender under synkroniseringen "
"som nye arrangementer, hvilket medfører, at der sendes en e-mailmeddelelse "
"fra Outlook til alle arrangementets deltagere."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:162
msgid ""
"To avoid unwanted emails being sent to all past, present, and future event "
"attendees, the user must add the events from the Odoo calendar to the "
"Outlook calendar before the first ever sync, delete the events from Odoo, "
"and then start the sync."
msgstr ""
"For at undgå uønskede e-mails sendt til alle tidligere, nuværende og "
"fremtidige arrangementdeltagere, skal brugeren tilføje arrangementerne fra "
"Odoo-kalenderen til Outlook-kalenderen før den allerførste synkronisering, "
"slette arrangementerne fra Odoo og derefter starte synkroniseringen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:166
msgid ""
"Even after synchronizing the Odoo Calendar with the Outlook calendar, "
"Outlook will still send a notification to all event participants every time "
"an event is edited (created, deleted, unarchived, or event date/time "
"changed), with no exceptions. This is a limitation that cannot be fixed from "
"Odoo's side."
msgstr ""
"Selv efter synkronisering af Odoo-kalenderen med Outlook-kalenderen vil "
"Outlook stadig sende en meddelelse til alle arrangementdeltagere, hver gang "
"et arrangement redigeres (oprettes, slettes, genaktiveres eller "
"arrangementsdato/-tid ændres), uden undtagelser. Dette er en begrænsning, "
"der ikke kan løses fra Odoo's side."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:171
msgid ""
"In summary, once a user synchronizes their Outlook calendar with the Odoo "
"calendar:"
msgstr ""
"Kort sagt, når en bruger synkroniserer deres Outlook-kalender med Odoo-"
"kalenderen:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:173
msgid ""
"Creating an event in Odoo causes Outlook to send an invitation to all event "
"attendees."
msgstr ""
"Oprettelse af et arrangement i Odoo får Outlook til at sende en invitation "
"til alle arrangementdeltagere."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:174
msgid ""
"Deleting an event in Odoo causes Outlook to send a cancellation to all event "
"attendees."
msgstr ""
"Sletning af et arrangement i Odoo får Outlook til at sende en aflysning til "
"alle arrangementdeltagere."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:175
msgid ""
"Unarchiving an event in Odoo causes Outlook to send an invitation to all "
"event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Genaktivering af et arrangement i Odoo får Outlook til at sende en "
"invitation til alle arrangementdeltagere."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:176
msgid ""
"Archiving an event in Odoo causes Outlook to send a cancellation to all "
"event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Arkivering af et arrangement i Odoo får Outlook til at sende en aflysning "
"til alle arrangementdeltagere."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:177
msgid ""
"Adding a contact to an event causes Outlook to send an invitation to all "
"event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Tilføjelse af en kontakt til et arrangement får Outlook til at sende en "
"invitation til alle arrangementdeltagere."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:178
msgid ""
"Removing a contact from an event causes Outlook to send a cancellation to "
"all event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Fjernelse af en kontakt fra et arrangement får Outlook til at sende en "
"aflysning til alle arrangementdeltagere."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:181
msgid "Sync Odoo Calendar and Outlook"
msgstr "Synkronisér Odoo-kalender og Outlook"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:183
msgid ""
"In the Odoo database, open to the *Calendar* module, and click "
"the :guilabel:`Outlook` sync button on the right-side of the page, beneath "
"the monthly calendar."
msgstr ""
"I Odoo-databasen, åbn modulet *Kalender*, og klik på :guilabel:`Outlook`-"
"synkroniseringsknappen på højre side af siden, under månedsoversigten."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "The \"Outlook\" sync button in Odoo Calendar."
msgstr "\"Outlook\"-synkroniseringsknappen i Odoo Kalender."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:190
msgid ""
"The synchronization is a two-way process, meaning that events are reconciled "
"in both accounts (*Outlook* and Odoo). The page redirects to a Microsoft "
"login page, and the user is asked to log in to their account, if they are "
"not already. Finally, grant the required permissions by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Accept`."
msgstr ""
"Synchronizace je obousměrný proces, což znamená, že události jsou "
"odsouhlaseny v obou účtech (*Outlook* a Odoo). Stránka přesměruje na "
"přihlašovací stránku Microsoftu a uživatel je požádán o přihlášení ke svému "
"účtu, pokud již není přihlášen. Nakonec udělte požadovaná oprávnění "
"kliknutím na :guilabel:`Přijmout`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "Authentication process on Microsoft Outlook OAuth page."
msgstr "Proces ověřování na stránce Microsoft Outlook OAuth."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:200
msgid ""
"All users that want to use the synchronization simply need to :ref:`sync "
"their calendar with Outlook <outlook/sync>`. The configuration of "
"Microsoft's *Azure* account is only done once, as Microsoft *Entra ID* "
"tenants' client IDs and client secrets are unique, and help the user manage "
"a specific instance of Microsoft cloud services for internal and external "
"users."
msgstr ""
"Všichni uživatelé, kteří chtějí používat synchronizaci, jednoduše "
"potřebují :ref:`synchronizovat svůj kalendář s Outlookem <outlook/sync>`. "
"Konfigurace účtu Microsoft *Azure* se provádí pouze jednou, protože ID "
"klientů a tajné klíče klientů tenantů Microsoft *Entra ID* jsou jedinečné a "
"pomáhají uživateli spravovat konkrétní instanci cloudových služeb Microsoftu "
"pro interní a externí uživatele."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:206
msgid ":doc:`../../general/integrations/mail_plugins/outlook`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../general/integrations/mail_plugins/outlook`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:207
msgid ":doc:`google`"
msgstr ":doc:`google`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:212
msgid ""
"There may be times when the *Microsoft Outlook Calendar* account does not "
"sync correctly with Odoo. Sync issues can be seen in the database logs."
msgstr ""
"Mohou nastat situace, kdy se účet *Microsoft Outlook Calendar* "
"nesynchronizuje správně s Odoo. Problémy se synchronizací lze vidět v "
"protokolech databáze."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:215
msgid ""
"In these cases, the account needs troubleshooting. A reset can be performed "
"using the :guilabel:`Reset Account` button, which can be accessed by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Manage Users`. Then, select "
"the user to modify the calendar, and click on the :guilabel:`Calendar` tab."
msgstr ""
"V těchto případech je třeba účet vyřešit. Reset lze provést pomocí "
"tlačítka :guilabel:`Resetovat účet`, ke kterému se dostanete tak, že "
"přejdete na :menuselection:`aplikace Nastavení --> Spravovat uživatele`. "
"Poté vyberte uživatele pro úpravu kalendáře a klikněte na "
"záložku :guilabel:`Kalendář`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:229
msgid ""
"The following reset options are available for troubleshooting *Microsoft "
"Outlook Calendar* sync with Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"Následující možnosti resetování jsou k dispozici pro řešení problémů se "
"synchronizací *Microsoft Outlook Calendar* s Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "Outlook calendar reset options in Odoo."
msgstr "Možnosti resetování kalendáře Outlook v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:239
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delete from the current Microsoft Calendar account`: delete the "
"events from *Microsoft Outlook Calendar*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Smazat z aktuálního účtu Microsoft Calendar`: smazat události z "
"*Microsoft Outlook Calendar*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:242
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delete from both`: delete the events from both *Microsoft Outlook "
"Calendar* and Odoo calendar."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Smazat z obou`: smazat události jak z *Microsoft Outlook "
"Calendar*, tak z kalendáře Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:247
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Synchronize only new events`: sync new events on *Microsoft "
"Outlook Calendar* and/or Odoo calendar."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Synchronizovat pouze nové události`: synchronizovat nové události "
"v *Microsoft Outlook Calendar* a/nebo kalendáři Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:249
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Synchronize all existing events`: sync all events on *Microsoft "
"Outlook Calendar* and/or Odoo calendar."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Synchronizovat všechny existující události`: synchronizovat "
"všechny události v *Microsoft Outlook Calendar* a/nebo kalendáři Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:5
msgid "Dashboards"
msgstr "Dashboards"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:13
msgid ""
"**Odoo Dashboards** allows you to consult, interact with, customize, and "
"build interactive dashboards that display real-time data from your Odoo "
"database in an easy-to-understand way. By centralizing data from various "
"Odoo sources in a single location, dashboards provide an overview of key "
"business metrics that can help you monitor business performance and make "
"informed decisions."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo Dashboards** giver dig mulighed for at konsultere, interagere med, "
"tilpasse og bygge interaktive dashboards, der viser realtidsdata fra din "
"Odoo-database på en letforståelig måde. Ved at centralisere data fra "
"forskellige Odoo-kilder ét sted giver dashboards et overblik over "
"nøgleforretningsmetrics, der kan hjælpe dig med at overvåge "
"forretningsresultater og træffe informerede beslutninger."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:18
msgid ""
":doc:`Odoo spreadsheets <../../applications/productivity/spreadsheet>` serve "
"as the foundation for dashboards, with tables and charts used to structure "
"and visualize dynamic Odoo data. :ref:`Data sources <spreadsheet/insert/data-"
"sources>` connect a dashboard's underlying spreadsheet to your database, "
"ensuring the most recent data is retrieved every time the dashboard is "
"opened or refreshed."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Odoo-regneark <../../applications/productivity/spreadsheet>` danner "
"grundlaget for dashboards, hvor tabeller og diagrammer bruges til at "
"strukturere og visualisere dynamiske Odoo-data. :ref:`Datakilder "
"<spreadsheet/insert/data-sources>` forbinder et dashboards underliggende "
"regneark til din database og sikrer, at de seneste data hentes, hver gang "
"dashboardet åbnes eller opdateres."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:24
msgid ""
"With Odoo Dashboards, users can, depending on their :ref:`access rights "
"<dashboards/access-and-sharing>`:"
msgstr ""
"Med Odoo Dashboards kan brugere, afhængigt af deres :ref:`adgangsrettigheder "
"<dashboards/access-and-sharing>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:27
msgid ""
":ref:`consult and interact with dashboards <dashboards/use-dashboards>`, "
"including :ref:`standard, pre-configured dashboards <dashboards/standard>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`konsultere og interagere med dashboards <dashboards/use-dashboards>`, "
"herunder :ref:`standard, prækonfigurerede dashboards <dashboards/standard>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:29
msgid ""
"use :ref:`global filters <dashboards/use-dashboards/global-filters>` to "
"filter all the data shown on a dashboard"
msgstr ""
"bruge :ref:`globale filtre <dashboards/use-dashboards/global-filters>` til "
"at filtrere alle data, der vises på et dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:31
msgid ""
":ref:`share a snapshot of a dashboard <dashboards/access-and-sharing>` with "
"internal users who do not have the appropriate access rights or with "
"external users"
msgstr ""
":ref:`dele et øjebliksbillede af et dashboard <dashboards/access-and-"
"sharing>` med interne brugere, der ikke har de passende adgangsrettigheder, "
"eller med eksterne brugere"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:33
msgid ""
":doc:`build custom dashboards <../../applications/productivity/dashboards/"
"build_and_customize_dashboards>` using Odoo Spreadsheet"
msgstr ""
":doc:`bygge tilpassede dashboards <../../applications/productivity/"
"dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards>` ved hjælp af Odoo Spreadsheet"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:36
msgid ""
":ref:`customize dashboards <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize>` to "
"modify what data is shown, the layout, or the filters available"
msgstr ""
":ref:`tilpasse dashboards <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize>` for at "
"ændre, hvilke data der vises, layoutet eller de tilgængelige filtre"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:38
msgid ""
":ref:`manage access rights <dashboards/access-and-sharing>` to dashboards"
msgstr ""
":ref:`administrere adgangsrettigheder <dashboards/access-and-sharing>` til "
"dashboards"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:39
msgid ""
"centralize frequently consulted Odoo views in a personal :doc:`../../"
"applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard`"
msgstr ""
"centralisere hyppigt konsulterede Odoo-visninger i et personligt :doc:`../../"
"applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:43
msgid ""
"Once a spreadsheet has been converted into a dashboard, it can only be "
"accessed via the Dashboards app."
msgstr ""
"Når et regneark er blevet konverteret til et dashboard, kan det kun tilgås "
"via Dashboards-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:45
msgid ""
"Unlike other Odoo dashboards, :guilabel:`My Dashboard` is not based on Odoo "
"Spreadsheet, but rather on :doc:`Odoo views <../studio/views>`."
msgstr ""
"I modsætning til andre Odoo-dashboards er :guilabel:`Mit Dashboard` ikke "
"baseret på Odoo Spreadsheet, men derimod på :doc:`Odoo-visninger <../studio/"
"views>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:51
msgid "Use dashboards"
msgstr "Brug dashboards"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:53
msgid ""
"When the Dashboards app is opened, the left panel lists all :ref:`standard, "
"pre-configured dashboards <dashboards/standard>` and :doc:`custom-built "
"dashboards <dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards>` to which a user has "
"been :ref:`granted access <dashboards/access-and-sharing>`, grouped by "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Když je otevřena aplikace Dashboards, levý panel zobrazuje "
"všechny :ref:`standardní, předkonfigurované dashboardy <dashboards/"
"standard>` a :doc:`vlastní dashboardy <dashboards/"
"build_and_customize_dashboards>`, ke kterým má uživatel :ref:`přidělen "
"přístup <dashboards/access-and-sharing>`, seskupené podle sekcí."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:58
msgid "Clicking on a dashboard name opens that dashboard in the main view."
msgstr ""
"Kliknutím na název dashboardu se otevře daný dashboard v hlavním zobrazení."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:None
msgid "Overview of Leads dashboard"
msgstr "Přehled dashboardu potenciálních zákazníků"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:64
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-angle-double-left` :guilabel:`(double chevron)` icon at "
"the top of the left panel to collapse the left panel, maximizing the space "
"available for dashboards."
msgstr ""
"Kliknutím na ikonu :icon:`fa-angle-double-left` :guilabel:`(dvojitá šipka)` "
"v horní části levého panelu sbalíte levý panel a maximalizujete prostor "
"dostupný pro dashboardy."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:66
msgid ""
"Mark a dashboard as a favorite by clicking the :icon:`fa-"
"star` :guilabel:`(Toggle favorite)` icon in the upper-right corner. "
"Favorited dashboards are grouped in a :guilabel:`Favorites` section at the "
"top of the left panel for easy access."
msgstr ""
"Označte dashboard jako oblíbený kliknutím na ikonu :icon:`fa-"
"star` :guilabel:`(Přepnout oblíbené)` v pravém horním rohu. Oblíbené "
"dashboardy jsou seskupeny v sekci :guilabel:`Oblíbené` v horní části levého "
"panelu pro snadný přístup."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:73
msgid "Filter and sort data"
msgstr "Filtrování a řazení dat"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:75
msgid ""
"Filtering and sorting allow you to manage what data is displayed and how it "
"is displayed. This can help tailor the view to answer specific business "
"questions."
msgstr ""
"Filtrování a řazení umožňují spravovat, jaká data jsou zobrazena a jak jsou "
"zobrazena. To může pomoci přizpůsobit zobrazení pro zodpovězení konkrétních "
"obchodních otázek."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:78
msgid ""
":ref:`Filtering <dashboards/use-dashboards/global-filters>` limits the data "
"presented in charts and tables, allowing you to focus only on records that "
"meet specific criteria,  e.g., viewing sales data only for a specific sales "
"team."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Filtrování <dashboards/use-dashboards/global-filters>` omezuje data "
"prezentovaná v grafech a tabulkách, což vám umožňuje zaměřit se pouze na "
"záznamy splňující specifická kritéria, např. zobrazení dat o prodeji pouze "
"pro konkrétní prodejní tým."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:81
msgid ""
":ref:`Sorting <dashboards/use-dashboards/sort>` reorders the data presented "
"in table columns, allowing you to see the data from different perspectives, "
"e.g., viewing products by sales revenue from highest to lowest."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Řazení <dashboards/use-dashboards/sort>` přeuspořádává data "
"prezentovaná ve sloupcích tabulky, což vám umožňuje vidět data z různých "
"perspektiv, např. zobrazení produktů podle prodejních výnosů od nejvyšších "
"po nejnižší."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:88
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/global_filters.rst:387
msgid "Apply global filters"
msgstr "Anvend globale filtre"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:90
msgid ""
"If :doc:`global filters <spreadsheet/work_with_data/global_filters>` have "
"been configured for a dashboard, a search bar is available above the "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Hvis :doc:`globale filtre <spreadsheet/work_with_data/global_filters>` er "
"konfigureret til et dashboard, er en søgelinje tilgængelig over dashboardet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:None
msgid "Global filters on the Project dashboard"
msgstr "Globale filtre på Projekt-dashboardet"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:98
msgid ""
"Global filters are available for all :ref:`standard dashboards <dashboards/"
"standard>`. Additional :doc:`global filters can be added <spreadsheet/"
"work_with_data/global_filters>` by a user with the appropriate :ref:`access "
"rights <dashboards/access-and-sharing/customize-configure-build>`."
msgstr ""
"Globální filtry jsou dostupné pro všechny :ref:`standardní dashboardy "
"<dashboards/standard>`. Další :doc:`globální filtry lze přidat <spreadsheet/"
"work_with_data/global_filters>` uživatelem s příslušnými :ref:`přístupovými "
"právy <dashboards/access-and-sharing/customize-configure-build>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:102
msgid ""
"It is also possible to :ref:`search for values <search/values>` by typing "
"directly in the search bar; the search categories shown reflect the "
"available global filters."
msgstr ""
"Je také možné :ref:`vyhledávat hodnoty <search/values>` přímým psaním do "
"vyhledávacího pole; zobrazené kategorie vyhledávání odrážejí dostupné "
"globální filtry."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:105
msgid "To apply global filters:"
msgstr "Použití globálních filtrů:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:107
msgid ""
"Click within the search bar or click on the :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(dropdown)` icon to access all filters available for that "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte do vyhledávacího pole nebo klikněte na ikonu :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(rozbalovací nabídka)` pro přístup ke všem filtrům "
"dostupným pro daný dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:109
msgid ""
"For the relevant filter, select a conditional operator from the first "
"dropdown, e.g., :guilabel:`is in`, then, as relevant, enter or select the "
"appropriate value."
msgstr ""
"For det relevante filter vælg en betinget operator fra den første dropdown, "
"f.eks. :guilabel:`is in`, og indtast eller vælg derefter den passende værdi "
"efter behov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:111
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/global_filters.rst:401
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Filter`."
msgstr "Klikněte na :guilabel:`Filtr`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:113
msgid ""
"For dashboards with a date filter, this filter can be set via the search bar "
"or via the button with the :icon:`fa-calendar` :guilabel:`(calendar)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Pro dashboardy s datumovým filtrem lze tento filtr nastavit prostřednictvím "
"vyhledávacího pole nebo pomocí tlačítka s ikonou :icon:`fa-"
"calendar` :guilabel:`(kalendář)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:None
msgid "Filtering a dashboard by date period"
msgstr "Filtrování dashboardu podle datumového období"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:119
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Custom Range` at the bottom of the period selector shows "
"either a manually entered custom range, if relevant, or the start and end "
"date of the selected period."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vlastní rozsah` v dolní části výběru období zobrazuje buď ručně "
"zadaný vlastní rozsah, pokud je relevantní, nebo datum začátku a konce "
"vybraného období."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:122
msgid ""
"To remove a value from a filter, click the :icon:`fa-"
"times` :guilabel:`(remove)` icon beside the name of the value; to empty a "
"filter, click the :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`(remove)` icon at the far "
"right of the filter."
msgstr ""
"Pro odstranění hodnoty z filtru klikněte na ikonu :icon:`fa-"
"times` :guilabel:`(odstranit)` vedle názvu hodnoty; pro vyprázdnění filtru "
"klikněte na ikonu :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`(odstranit)` úplně vpravo u "
"filtru."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:129
msgid "Sort data"
msgstr "Řazení dat"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:131
msgid ""
"Depending on the dashboard and the table in question, it may be possible to "
"sort the data by column, by clicking the column heading. A :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(caret down)` or :icon:`fa-caret-up` :guilabel:`(caret up)` "
"icon beside a column heading indicates that the column has been sorted in "
"descending or ascending order, respectively. If, when hovering over other "
"column headings, a :icon:`fa-sort` :guilabel:`(sort)` icon appears, the "
"column can be sorted."
msgstr ""
"V závislosti na dashboardu a dané tabulce může být možné řadit data podle "
"sloupce kliknutím na záhlaví sloupce. Ikona :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(šipka dolů)` nebo :icon:`fa-caret-up` :guilabel:`(šipka "
"nahoru)` vedle záhlaví sloupce označuje, že sloupec byl seřazen v sestupném "
"nebo vzestupném pořadí. Pokud se při najetí na jiná záhlaví sloupců zobrazí "
"ikona :icon:`fa-sort` :guilabel:`(řadit)`, sloupec lze řadit."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:138
msgid ""
"If conditional formatting has been applied to a table, the original "
"formatting is maintained when the table is resorted by a different column."
msgstr ""
"Pokud bylo na tabulku použito podmíněné formátování, původní formátování "
"zůstane zachováno, když je tabulka znovu seřazena podle jiného sloupce."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:142
msgid ""
"In this example, the table was originally sorted by revenue per CRM tag, in "
"decreasing order. Conditional formatting was defined to visualize the "
"proportional revenue using data bars. When the table is resorted by number "
"of leads in descending order, the data bars still reflect the revenue per "
"tag in decreasing order."
msgstr ""
"V tomto příkladu byla tabulka původně seřazena podle příjmů na CRM značku v "
"klesajícím pořadí. Podmíněné formátování bylo definováno tak, aby "
"vizualizovalo proporcionální příjmy pomocí datových pruhů. Když je tabulka "
"znovu seřazena podle počtu potenciálních zákazníků v sestupném pořadí, "
"datové pruhy stále odrážejí příjmy na značku v klesajícím pořadí."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:0
msgid "Sorting a table with conditional formatting using data bars"
msgstr "Řazení tabulky s podmíněným formátováním pomocí datových pruhů"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:154
msgid "Access underlying records"
msgstr "Přístup k podkladovým záznamům"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:156
msgid ""
"While dashboards provide a user-friendly summary of key data, drilling down "
"to the underlying data allows a more detailed analysis. This can be useful "
"for investigating anomalies or providing the full context needed for "
"decision-making."
msgstr ""
"Zatímco dashboardy poskytují uživatelsky přívětivý přehled klíčových dat, "
"rozbalení k podkladovým datům umožňuje detailnější analýzu. To může být "
"užitečné pro vyšetřování anomálií nebo poskytnutí úplného kontextu "
"potřebného pro rozhodování."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:160
msgid ""
"**Open underlying database records**: To access database records referenced "
"by a dashboard, click on the relevant value in a table or on a data point on "
"a chart. Doing so opens either the individual record, or, in the case of "
"charts or tables displaying consolidated data, a list of the referenced "
"records."
msgstr ""
"**Åbn underliggende databaseposter**: For at få adgang til databaseposter, "
"der refereres af et dashboard, skal du klikke på den relevante værdi i en "
"tabel eller på et datapunkt på et diagram. Dette åbner enten den enkelte "
"post eller, i tilfælde af diagrammer eller tabeller, der viser konsoliderede "
"data, en liste over de refererede poster."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:165
msgid ""
"**Open underlying database views**: To access the view from which the data "
"for a specific chart or table is retrieved, click on the title of the chart "
"or table. Doing so opens the corresponding list view, pivot view or graph "
"view."
msgstr ""
"**Åbn underliggende databasevisninger**: For at få adgang til den visning, "
"hvorfra dataene for et specifikt diagram eller tabel hentes, skal du klikke "
"på titlen på diagrammet eller tabellen. Dette åbner den tilsvarende "
"listevisning, pivotvisning eller grafvisning."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:170
msgid ""
"To return to a dashboard after drilling down to underlying records or views, "
"click the :guilabel:`Dashboards` breadcrumb in the upper-left corner."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li se vrátit na dashboard po rozbalení k podkladovým záznamům nebo "
"pohledům, klikněte na navigační odkaz :guilabel:`Dashboards` v levém horním "
"rohu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:176
msgid "Expand, copy or download charts"
msgstr "Rozbalení, kopírování nebo stažení grafů"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:178
msgid ""
"To see charts in full screen, hover over a chart and click the :icon:`fa-"
"expand` icon."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li zobrazit grafy na celou obrazovku, najeďte na graf a klikněte na "
"ikonu :icon:`fa-expand`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:180
msgid ""
"It is also possible to copy or download a chart by hovering over the chart "
"and clicking the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (vertical ellipsis) icon, then "
"clicking :icon:`os-copy-as-image` :guilabel:`Copy as image` or :icon:`fa-"
"download` :guilabel:`Download` as relevant."
msgstr ""
"Je také možné zkopírovat nebo stáhnout graf najetím na graf a kliknutím na "
"ikonu :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (svislé tři tečky), poté kliknutím na :icon:`os-"
"copy-as-image` :guilabel:`Kopírovat jako obrázek` nebo :icon:`fa-"
"download` :guilabel:`Stáhnout` podle potřeby."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:185
msgid ""
":ref:`Expanding a time-series chart to full screen <dashboards/use-"
"dashboards/time-series-charts-zoom-scroll>` allows a more detailed analysis."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Rozbalení časového grafu na celou obrazovku <dashboards/use-dashboards/"
"time-series-charts-zoom-scroll>` umožňuje detailnější analýzu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:191
msgid "Analyze time-series charts"
msgstr "Analýza časových grafů"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:193
msgid ""
"Time-series charts, i.e., charts showing data over time, can be analyzed "
"more closely by:"
msgstr ""
"Časové grafy, tj. grafy zobrazující data v čase, lze analyzovat podrobněji:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:195
msgid ""
":ref:`adjusting the granularity <dashboards/use-dashboards/time-series-"
"charts-granularity>`;"
msgstr ""
":ref:`úpravou granularity <dashboards/use-dashboards/time-series-charts-"
"granularity>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:196
msgid ""
":ref:`zooming in <dashboards/use-dashboards/time-series-charts-zoom-scroll>` "
"on a chosen time span."
msgstr ""
":ref:`přiblížením <dashboards/use-dashboards/time-series-charts-zoom-"
"scroll>` na zvolené časové období."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:202
msgid "Adjust granularity"
msgstr "Úprava granularity"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:204
msgid ""
"For many time-series charts it is possible to adjust the granularity of the "
"unit of time on the x-axis."
msgstr ""
"U mnoha časových grafů je možné upravit granularitu časové jednotky na ose x."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:207
msgid ""
"To do so, hover over the chart, click the :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(dropdown)` icon, then select the desired granularity."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li to provést, najeďte na graf, klikněte na ikonu :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(rozbalovací nabídka)`, poté vyberte požadovanou "
"granularitu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:None
msgid "Changing time granularity on a chart's y-axis"
msgstr "Změna časové granularity na ose y grafu"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:217
msgid "Zoom in on a time span and scroll"
