"account on `Axivox <https://manage.axivox.com/>`__. Replace `YOURACCOUNT` "
"with the company account name."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`OnSIP-domæne`: det domæne, der blev tildelt ved oprettelse af en "
"konto på `Axivox <https://manage.axivox.com/>`__. Erstat `YOURACCOUNT` med "
"virksomhedens kontonavn."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/axivox_config.rst:49
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/didww.rst:92
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/onsip.rst:54
msgid ":guilabel:`VoIP Environment`: select :guilabel:`Production`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`VoIP-miljø`: vælg :guilabel:`Produktion`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/axivox_config.rst:None
