msgstr ":guilabel:`Hemmelighed`: Axivox :guilabel:`SIP-adgangskode`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/axivox_config.rst:70
msgid ""
"Make sure to manually type the :guilabel:`SIP password` into the "
