"<spreadsheet/global-filters/create-types>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/global_filters.rst:380
msgid ""
"**Delete a global filter** by clicking the :icon:`fa-trash` icon on the "
"relevant card. Alternatively, with a filter's :guilabel:`Filter properties` "
"panel open, click :guilabel:`Remove` to delete the global filter."
msgstr ""
"**Smažte globální filtr** kliknutím na ikonu :icon:`fa-trash` na příslušné "
"kartě. Případně s otevřeným panelem :guilabel:`Vlastnosti filtru` klikněte "
"na :guilabel:`Odstranit` pro smazání globálního filtru."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/global_filters.rst:389
msgid "To apply global filters in a spreadsheet:"
msgstr "Aplikace globálních filtrů v tabulce:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/global_filters.rst:391
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`os-global-filters` :guilabel:`Filters` icon at the top "
"right of the spreadsheet. The :guilabel:`Global Filters` pop-up window "
"displays the available global filters."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na ikonu :icon:`os-global-filters` :guilabel:`Filtry` v pravém "
"horním rohu tabulky. Dialogové okno :guilabel:`Globální filtry` zobrazí "
"dostupné globální filtry."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/global_filters.rst:395
msgid ""
"If no global filters have been configured for the spreadsheet, "
